# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-104">Entitetsdefinitioner för typer av känslig information</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-108">ABA-routningsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-108">ABA routing number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-110">Nio siffror som kan vara i ett formaterat eller oformaterat mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-110">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-114">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-114">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-115">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-115">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-116">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-116">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-117">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-117">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-118">Oformaterade: nio siffror i följd som börjar med 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 eller 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-118">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-120">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-120">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-121">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-122">En princip har med medelhög säkerhet upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om, inom 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-122">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-123">Funktionen för Func_aba_routing hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-123">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-124">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ABA_Routing hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-124">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-125">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-125">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-126">Funktionen för Func_aba_routing hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-126">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-144">Argentinas national identity (DNI) number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-144">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-145">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-145">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-146">Åtta siffror med eller utan punkter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-146">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-147">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-147">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-148">Åtta siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-148">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-149">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-149">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-150">en valfri period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-150">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-151">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-151">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-152">en valfri period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-152">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-153">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-153">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-154">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-154">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-155">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-155">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-156">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-156">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-157">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-157">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-158">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_argentina_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-158">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-159">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_argentina_national_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-159">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-unique-tax-identification-key-cuitcuil"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-171">Argentinas unika skatteidentifieringsnyckel (CUIT/CUIL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-171">Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-172">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-172">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-173">Elva siffror med streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-173">Eleven digits with dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-174">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-174">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-175">Elva siffror med ett streck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-175">Eleven digits with a dash:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-176">två siffror i 20, 23, 24, 27, 30, 33 eller 34</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-176">two digits in 20, 23, 24, 27, 30, 33 or 34</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-177">ett bindestreck (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-177">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-178">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-178">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-179">ett bindestreck (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-179">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-180">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-180">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-181">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-181">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-182">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-182">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-183">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-183">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-184">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-184">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-185">Funktionen hittar `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-185">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-186">Ett nyckelord `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-186">A keyword from `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-187">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-187">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-188">Funktionen hittar `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-188">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL) -->
      <Entity id="98da3da1-9199-4571-b7c4-b6522980b507" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-227">Bankkontonummer för Australien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-227">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-228">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-228">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-229">Sex till tio siffror med eller utan ett bankkontornummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-229">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-230">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-230">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-231">Kontonumret kan vara 6 till 10 siffror.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-231">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-232">Bankkontor i Australien:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-232">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-233">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-233">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-234">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-234">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-235">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-235">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-236">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-237">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-237">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-238">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-239">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-239">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-240">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_australia_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-240">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-241">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_australia_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-241">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-242">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-242">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-243">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-243">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-244">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_australia_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-244">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-245">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_australia_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-245">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

      </Entity>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-318">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-318">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-319">Funktionen för Func_Australian_Company_Number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-319">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml

      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-329">Australiens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-329">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-330">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-330">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-331">nio bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-331">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-332">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-332">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-333">Nio bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-333">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-334">två siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-334">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-335">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-335">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-336">Fem siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-336">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-337">ELLER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-337">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-338">En till två valfria bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-338">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-339">fyra till nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-339">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-340">ELLER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-340">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-341">nio siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-341">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-342">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-342">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-343">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-343">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-344">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-344">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-345">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-345">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-346">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_australia_drivers_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-346">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-347">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-347">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-348">Inget nyckelord från Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-348">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-448">Australiens medicinska kontonummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-448">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-449">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-449">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-450">10–11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-450">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-451">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-451">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-452">10–11 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-452">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-453">Den första siffran i intervallet 2–6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-453">First digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-454">Nio siffror är en kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-454">Nine digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-455">Tionde siffran är problemets siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-455">Tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-456">Elfte siffran (valfritt) är det enskilda talet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-456">Eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-457">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-457">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-458">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-458">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-459">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-459">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-460">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-460">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-461">Funktionen för Func_australian_medical_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-461">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-462">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-462">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-463">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-463">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-475">Australien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-475">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-476">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-476">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-477">En bokstav följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-477">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-478">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-478">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-479">En bokstav (inte en case-sensitive) följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-479">A letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-480">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-480">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-481">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-481">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-482">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-482">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-483">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-483">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-484">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_australia_passport_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-484">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-485">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_passport eller Keyword_australia_passport_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-485">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-519">Australiens skattenummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-519">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-520">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-520">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-521">åtta till nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-521">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-522">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-522">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-523">Åtta till nio siffror visas vanligtvis med blanksteg enligt följande:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-523">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-524">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-524">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-525">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-525">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-526">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-526">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-527">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-527">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-528">Två till tre siffror där den sista siffran är en bård</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-528">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-529">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-530">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-530">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-531">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-532">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-532">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-533">Funktionen för Func_australian_tax_file_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-533">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-534">Inget nyckelord från Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number eller Keyword_number_exclusions hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-534">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-535">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-535">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-536">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-536">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-547">Österrikes körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-547">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-548">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-548">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-549">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-549">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-550">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-550">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-551">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-551">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-552">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-552">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-553">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-553">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-554">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-554">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-555">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-555">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-556">Det reguljära  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-556">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-557">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-557">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-684">Österrike-identitetskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-684">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-685">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-685">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-686">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-686">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-687">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-687">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-688">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-688">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-689">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-689">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-690">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-690">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-691">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-691">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-692">En kombination av bokstäver, siffror och specialtecken med 24 tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-692">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-693">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-693">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-694">24 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-694">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-695">22 bokstäver (inte versaler, siffror, omslag, snedstreck eller plustecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-695">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-696">Två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga), siffror, omslag, snedstreck, plustecken eller likhetstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-696">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-697">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-697">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-698">Ej tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-698">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-699">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-699">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-700">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-700">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-701">Det reguljära  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-701">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-702">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-702">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-703">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-703">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-704">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-704">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-708">Österrike passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-708">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-709">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-709">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-710">En bokstav följt av ett valfritt blanksteg och sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-710">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-711">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-711">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-712">En kombination av en bokstav, sju siffror och ett blanksteg:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-712">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-713">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-713">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-714">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-714">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-715">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-715">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-716">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-716">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-717">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-717">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-718">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-718">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-719">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-719">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-720">Det reguljära  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-720">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-721">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-721">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-722">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-722">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-723">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-723">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-724">Det reguljära  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-724">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-725">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-725">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-742">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-742">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-749">Österrikes personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-749">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-750">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-750">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-751">10 siffror i det angivna formatet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-751">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-752">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-752">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-753">10 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-753">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-754">Tre siffror som motsvarar ett serienummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-754">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-755">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-755">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-756">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-756">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-757">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-757">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-758">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-758">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-759">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-759">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-760">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-760">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-761">Funktionen hittar  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-761">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-762">ett nyckelord  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-762">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-763">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-763">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-764">Funktionen hittar  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-764">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-765">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-765">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-766">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-766">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-767">österrike ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-767">austrian ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-768">ehic number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-768">ehic number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-769">ehic no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-769">ehic no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-770">insurance code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-770">insurance code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-771">insurancecode #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-771">insurancecode#</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-790">Österrikes skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-790">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-791">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-791">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-792">Nio siffror med valfritt bindestreck och snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-792">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-793">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-793">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-794">Nio siffror med valfritt bindestreck och snedstreck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-794">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-795">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-795">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-796">Ett bindestreck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-796">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-797">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-797">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-798">ett snedstreck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-798">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-799">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-799">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-800">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-800">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-801">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-801">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-802">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-802">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-803">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-803">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-804">Funktionen hittar  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-804">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-805">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-805">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-806">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-806">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-807">Funktionen hittar  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-807">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-830">Moms i Österrike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-830">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-831">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-831">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-832">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-832">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-833">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-833">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-834">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-834">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-835">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-835">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-836">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-836">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-837">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-838">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 11 tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-838">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-839">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-840">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 11 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-840">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-841">A eller a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-841">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-842">T eller t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-842">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-843">Valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-843">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-844">U eller u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-844">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-845">valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-845">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-846">två eller tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-846">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-847">valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-847">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-848">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-848">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-849">valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-849">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-850">en eller två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-850">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-851">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-851">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-852">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-852">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-853">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-853">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-854">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-854">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-855">Funktionen för Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-855">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-856">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-856">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-857">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-857">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-858">Funktionen för Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-858">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-876">Azure DocumentDB-autentiseringsnyckel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-876">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-877">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-877">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-878">Strängen "DocumentDb" följt av de tecken och strängar som beskrivs i mönstret nedan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-878">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-879">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-879">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-880">Strängen "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-880">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-881">Valfri kombination av 3–200 gemener eller versaler, siffror, symboler, specialtecken eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-881">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-882">En större än-symbol (>), ett likhetstecken (=), ett citattecken ("), eller en apostrof (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-882">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-883">Valfri kombination av 86 gemener eller versaler, siffror, snedstreck (/) eller plustecken (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-883">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-884">Två likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-884">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-907">Strängen "Server", "server" eller "datakälla" följt av de tecken och strängar som beskrivs i mönstret nedan, inklusive strängen "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-907">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-908">com" eller "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-908">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-909">net" eller "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-909">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-910">net" och strängen "Lösenord" eller "lösenord" eller "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-910">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-914">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-914">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-915">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-915">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-924">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-924">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-987">Lösenord för Azure-publiceringsinställning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-987">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-988">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-988">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-989">Strängen "userpwd=" följt av en alfanumerisk sträng.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-989">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-990">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-990">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-991">strängen "userpwd="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-991">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-992">valfri kombination av 60 gemener eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-992">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-993">ett citattecken (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-993">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-994">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-994">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-995">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-995">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-996">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-996">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-997">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-997">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-998">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-998">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-999">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_CommonExampleKeywords hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-999">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1018">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1018">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1024">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1024">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1025">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1025">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1026">valfri kombination av 43 tecken som är gemener eller versaler, siffror, snedstreck (/) eller plustecken (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1026">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1027">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1027">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1032">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1032">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1033">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_CommonExampleKeywords hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1033">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1048">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1048">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1049">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1049">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1050">Strängen "sig" följt av de tecken och strängar som beskrivs i mönstret nedan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1050">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1053">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1053">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1055">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1055">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1060">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1060">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1061">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1061">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1062">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1062">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1063">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzureSAS hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1063">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1085">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1086">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1086">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1087">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1087">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1088">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_CommonExampleKeywords hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1088">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1103">Azure Storage Account-nyckel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1103">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1104">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1104">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1105">Strängen "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" följt av de tecken och strängar som beskrivs i mönstret nedan, inklusive strängen "AccountKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1105">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1106">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1106">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1107">strängen "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1107">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1108">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1108">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1109">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1109">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1110">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1110">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1111">valfri kombination av 1–200 gemener eller versaler, siffror, symboler, specialtecken eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1111">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1112">strängen "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1112">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1113">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1113">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1114">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1114">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1115">noll till två blankstegstecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1115">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1116">valfri kombination av 86 tecken som är gemener eller versaler, siffror, snedstreck (/) eller plustecken (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1116">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1117">två likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1117">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1118">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1119">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1119">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1120">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1121">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1121">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1122">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1122">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1123">Det reguljära CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1123">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1124">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_CommonExampleKeywords hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1124">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
