## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1142">Azure Storage (allmän)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1142">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1143">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1143">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1144">Valfri kombination av 86 gemener eller versaler, siffror, snedstreck (/) eller plustecken (+), före eller efter tecknen som beskrivs i mönstret nedan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1144">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1145">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1145">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1146">noll till ett av symbolen större än (>), apostrof ('), likhetstecken (=), citattecken (") eller nummertecken (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1146">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1147">valfri kombination av 86 tecken som är gemener eller versaler, siffror, snedstreck (/) eller plustecken (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1147">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1148">två likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1148">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1149">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1149">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1150">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1150">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1151">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1151">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1152">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1152">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1153">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1153">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1154">Belgiens licensnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1154">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1155">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1155">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1156">10 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1156">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1157">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1157">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1158">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1158">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1159">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1159">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1160">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1160">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1161">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1161">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1162">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1162">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1163">Det reguljära  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1163">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1164">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1164">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1297">Belgiens nationalnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1297">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1298">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1298">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1299">11 siffror plus valfria avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1299">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1300">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1300">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1301">11 siffror plus avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1301">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1302">Sex siffror och två valfria punkter i formatet YY. MM.DD för födelsedatum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1302">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1303">En valfri avgränsare från punkt, streck, blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1303">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1304">Tre siffror i följd (udda för män, även för kvinnor)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1304">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1305">En valfri avgränsare från punkt, streck, blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1305">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1306">två kontrollsiffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1306">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1307">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1307">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1308">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1308">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1309">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1309">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1310">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1310">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1311">Funktionen för Func_belgium_national_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1311">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1312">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_belgium_national_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1312">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1313">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1313">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1314">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1314">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1315">Funktionen för Func_belgium_national_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1315">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1316">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1316">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1375">Belgien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1375">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1376">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1376">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1377">Två bokstäver följt av sex siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1377">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1378">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1378">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1379">Två bokstäver och följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1379">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1380">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1380">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1381">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1381">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1382">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1382">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1383">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1383">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1384">Det reguljära  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1384">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1385">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1385">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1386">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date2` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD MM YY eller ett nyckelord från eller `Keywords_eu_passport_date` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1386">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1387">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1387">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1388">Det reguljära  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1388">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1389">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1389">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1416">Nummer för moms för belgien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1416">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1417">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1417">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1418">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1418">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1419">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1419">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1420">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1420">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1421">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1421">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1422">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1422">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1423">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1423">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1424">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 12 tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1424">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1425">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1425">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1426">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 12 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1426">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1427">a bokstaven B eller b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1427">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1428">ett bokstaven E eller e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1428">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1429">en siffra 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1429">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1430">en siffra mellan 1 och 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1430">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1431">En valfri punkt eller ett bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1431">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1432">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1432">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1433">En valfri punkt eller ett bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1433">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1434">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1434">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1435">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1435">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1436">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1436">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1437">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1437">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1438">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1438">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1439">Funktionen Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1439">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1440">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1440">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1441">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1441">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1442">Funktionen Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1442">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1443">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1443">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1444">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1444">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1447">momsnr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1447">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1448">numéro t.v.a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1448">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1449">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1449">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1450">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1450">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1451">han/hon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1451">btw</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1452">han/hon #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1452">btw#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1453">moms #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1453">vat#</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1454">Brasiliens CPF-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1454">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1456">11 siffror som innehåller en bediff och kan formateras eller vara oformaterade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1456">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1457">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1458">Formaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1458">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1459">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1459">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1460">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1460">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1461">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1461">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1462">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1462">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1463">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1463">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1464">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1464">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1465">två siffror som anger siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1465">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1466">Oformaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1466">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1467">11 siffror där de två sista siffrorna är kontrollsiffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1467">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1468">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1468">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1469">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1469">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1470">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1470">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1471">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1471">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1472">Funktionen för Func_brazil_cpf hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1472">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1473">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_brazil_cpf hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1473">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1474">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1474">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1475">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1475">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1476">Funktionen för Func_brazil_cpf hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1476">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1477">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1477">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1478">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1478">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1479">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1479">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1480">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1480">CPF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1482">Registrering</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1482">Registration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1483">Intäkter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1483">Revenue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1484">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1484">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1485">Imposto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1485">Imposto</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1486">Identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1486">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1487">Inscrição</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1487">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1488">Receita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1488">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1489">Brasiliens juridiska enhetsnummer (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1489">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1490">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1490">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1491">14 siffror som innehåller ett registreringsnummer, branchnummer och kontrollera siffror, plus avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1491">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1492">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1492">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1493">14 siffror plus avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1493">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1494">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1494">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1495">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1495">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1496">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1496">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1497">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1497">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1498">tre siffror (de åtta första siffrorna är registreringsnumret)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1498">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1499">ett snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1499">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1500">fyrsiffrigt branchnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1500">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1501">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1501">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1502">två siffror som anger siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1502">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1503">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1503">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1504">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1504">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1505">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1505">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1506">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1506">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1507">Funktionen för Func_brazil_cnpj hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1507">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1508">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_brazil_cnpj hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1508">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1509">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1509">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1510">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1511">Funktionen för Func_brazil_cnpj hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1511">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1512">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1512">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1513">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1513">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1514">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1514">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1515">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1515">CNPJ</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1516">CNPJ/MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1516">CNPJ/MF</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1517">CNPJ-MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1517">CNPJ-MF</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1518">National Registry of Legal Entities</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1518">National Registry of Legal Entities</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1519">Taxpayers Registry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1519">Taxpayers Registry</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1534">Brasiliens national identification card (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1534">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1535">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1535">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1536">Registro Geral (gammalt format): Nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1536">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1537">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (nytt format): 11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1537">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1538">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1539">Registro Geral (gammalt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1539">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1540">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1540">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1541">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1541">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1542">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1542">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1543">en punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1543">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1544">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1544">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1545">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1545">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1546">en siffra som är en biffrig siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1546">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1547">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (nytt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1547">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1548">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1548">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1549">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1549">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1550">en siffra som är en biffrig siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1550">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1551">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1551">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1552">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1552">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1553">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1553">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1554">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1554">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1555">Funktionen för Func_brazil_rg hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1555">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1556">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_brazil_rg hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1556">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1557">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1557">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1560">Sådär de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1560">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1561">identitetskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1561">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1562">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1562">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1563">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1563">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1564">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1564">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1565">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1565">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1566">RG (det här nyckelordet är fallkänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1566">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1567">RIC (det här nyckelordet är fallkänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1567">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1568">Bulgariens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1568">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1569">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1569">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1570">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1570">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1571">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1571">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1572">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1572">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1573">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1573">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1574">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1574">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1575">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1575">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1576">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1576">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1577">Det reguljära  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1577">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1578">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1578">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1705">Bulgariens enhetliga civilnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1705">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1706">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1706">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1707">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1707">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1708">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1708">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1709">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1709">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1710">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1710">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1711">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1711">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1712">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1712">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1713">10 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1713">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1714">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1714">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1715">10 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1715">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1716">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (AMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1716">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1717">två siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1717">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1718">en siffra som motsvarar kön: En jämn siffra för man och en udda siffra för kvinna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1718">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1719">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1719">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1720">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1720">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1721">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1721">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1722">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1722">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1723">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1723">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1724">Funktionen hittar  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1724">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1725">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1725">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1726">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1726">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1727">Funktionen hittar  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1727">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1772">Bulgarien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1772">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1773">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1773">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1774">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1774">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1775">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1775">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1776">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1776">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1777">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1777">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1778">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1778">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1779">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1779">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1780">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1780">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1781">Det reguljära  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1781">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1782">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1782">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1783">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1783">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1784">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1784">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1785">Det reguljära  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1785">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1786">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1786">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1806">Bankkontonummer för Kanada</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1806">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1807">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1807">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1808">7 eller 12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1808">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1809">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1809">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1810">Ett bankkontonummer i Kanada har 7 eller 12 siffror.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1810">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1811">Ett bankkontotransitnummer för Kanada är:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1811">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1812">fem siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1812">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1813">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1813">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1814">tre siffror ELLER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1814">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1815">en nolla "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1815">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1816">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1816">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1817">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1817">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1818">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1818">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1819">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1819">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1820">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1820">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1821">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1821">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1822">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_canada_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1822">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1823">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1823">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1824">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1824">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1825">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1825">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1826">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_canada_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1826">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1857">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1857">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1858">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1858">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1859">Funktionen Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1859">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1860">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1860">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1861">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_canada_drivers_license hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1861">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1997">Kanadas hälsotjänstnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1997">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1998">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1998">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-1999">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-1999">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2000">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2000">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2001">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2001">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2002">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2002">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2003">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2003">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2004">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2004">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2005">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2005">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2006">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_health_service_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2006">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2007">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_canada_health_service_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2007">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2019">Kanada passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2019">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2020">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2021">Två versaler följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2021">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2024">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2024">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2025">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2025">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2026">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2026">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2027">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2027">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2028">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_passport_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2028">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2029">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_canada_passport_number eller Keyword_passport hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2029">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2059">Canada Personal Health Identification Number (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2059">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2060">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2060">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2061">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2061">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2062">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2062">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2063">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2063">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2064">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2064">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2065">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2065">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2066">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2066">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2067">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2067">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2068">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_canada_phin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2068">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2069">Minst två nyckelord från Keyword_canada_phin eller Keyword_canada_provinces hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2069">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2102">Kanadas socialförsäkringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2102">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2103">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2103">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2104">Nio siffror med valfria bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2104">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2105">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2105">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2106">Formaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2106">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2107">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2107">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2108">Ett bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2108">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2109">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2109">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2110">Ett bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2110">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2111">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2111">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2112">Oformaterad: nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2112">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2113">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2113">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2114">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2114">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2115">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2115">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2116">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2116">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2117">Funktionen för Func_canadian_sin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2117">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2118">Minst två av följande kombinationer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2118">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2119">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_sin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2119">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2120">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_sin_collaborative hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2120">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2121">Funktionen Func_eu_date hittar ett datum i rätt datumformat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2121">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2122">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2122">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2123">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2123">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2124">Funktionen för Func_unformatted_canadian_sin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2124">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2125">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_sin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2125">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2126">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2126">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2151">Chiles identitetskortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2151">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2152">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2152">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2153">sju till åtta siffror plus avgränsare en kontrollerad siffra eller bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2153">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2154">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2154">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2155">sju till åtta siffror plus avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2155">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2156">En till två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2156">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2157">en valfri period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2157">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2158">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2158">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2159">en valfri period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2159">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2160">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2160">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2161">ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2161">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2162">en siffra eller bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig) som är en kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2162">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2163">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2164">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2164">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2165">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2166">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2166">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2167">Funktionen för Func_chile_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2167">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2168">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_chile_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2168">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2169">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2169">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2170">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2170">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2171">Funktionen för Func_chile_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2171">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2172">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2172">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
