## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2209">Inhörande identitetskort (Folkrepubliken Kina) i Kina</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2209">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2210">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2210">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2211">18 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2211">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2212">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2212">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2213">18 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2213">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2214">Sex siffror som är en adresskod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2214">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2215">Åtta siffror i formuläret YYYYMMDD, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2215">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2216">tre siffror som är en orderkod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2216">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2217">en siffra som är en biffrig siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2217">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2218">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2218">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2219">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2219">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2220">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2220">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2221">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2221">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2222">Funktionen för Func_china_resident_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2222">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2223">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_china_resident_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2223">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2224">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2224">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2225">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2225">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2226">Funktionen för Func_china_resident_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2226">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2227">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2227">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2235">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2235">居民身份证</span></span>

## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2240">Kreditkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2240">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2241">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2242">14 till 16 siffror som kan vara formaterade eller oformaterade (ddddddddddd) och som måste passera Luhn-testet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2242">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2243">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2244">Komplext och robust mönster som identifierar kort från alla större varumärken över hela världen, inklusive Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, presentkort och betalkort.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2244">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2245">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2246">Ja, Luhn-kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2246">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2247">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2248">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2248">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2249">Funktionen Func_credit_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2249">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2250">Något av följande är sant:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2250">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2251">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_cc_verification hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2251">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2252">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_cc_name hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2252">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2253">Funktionen Func_expiration_date hittar ett datum i rätt datumformat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2253">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2254">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2254">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2255">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2255">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2256">Funktionen Func_credit_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2256">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2257">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2257">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2517">Kroatiens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2517">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2518">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2518">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2519">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2519">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2520">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2520">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2521">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2521">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2522">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2522">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2523">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2523">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2524">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2524">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2525">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2525">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2526">Det reguljära  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2526">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2527">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2527">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2651">Kroatiens identitetskortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2651">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2652">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i den nationella identifieringstypen (EU).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2652">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2653">Det är tillgängligt som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2653">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2654">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2654">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2655">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2655">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2656">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2656">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2657">nio siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2657">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2658">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2658">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2659">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2659">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2660">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2660">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2661">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2661">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2662">Funktionen för Func_croatia_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2662">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2663">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_croatia_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2663">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2694">Kroatien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2694">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2696">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2696">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2697">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2698">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2698">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2699">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2699">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2700">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2700">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2701">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2701">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2702">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2702">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2703">Det reguljära  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2703">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2704">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2704">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2705">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2705">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2706">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2706">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2707">Det reguljära  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2707">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2708">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2708">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2709">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2709">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2726">Kroatiens id-nummer (OIB)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2726">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2727">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2727">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2728">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2728">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2729">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2729">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2730">11 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2730">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2731">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2731">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2732">slutsiffra är en kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2732">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2733">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2733">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2734">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2734">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2735">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2735">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2736">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2736">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2737">Funktionen för Func_croatia_oib_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2737">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2738">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2738">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2739">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2739">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2740">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2740">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2741">Funktionen för Func_croatia_oib_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2741">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2742">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2742">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2773">Licensnummer för cyperns drivrutiner</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2773">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2774">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2774">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2775">12 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2775">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2776">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2776">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2777">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2777">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2778">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2778">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2779">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2779">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2780">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2780">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2781">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2782">Det reguljära  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2782">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2783">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2783">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2908">Identitetskort för Cypern</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2908">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2909">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2909">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2910">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2910">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2911">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2911">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2912">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2912">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2913">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2913">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2914">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2914">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2915">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2915">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2916">10 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2916">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2917">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2917">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2918">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2918">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2919">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2919">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2920">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2920">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2921">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2921">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2922">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2922">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2923">Det reguljära  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2923">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2924">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2924">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2925">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2925">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2933">Cypern passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2933">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2934">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2934">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2935">en bokstav följt av 6–8 siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2935">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2936">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2936">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2937">en bokstav följt av sex till åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2937">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2938">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2939">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2939">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2940">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2941">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2941">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2942">Det reguljära  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2942">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2943">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2944">Det reguljära `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD/MM/YYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2944">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2945">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2945">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2946">Det reguljära  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2946">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2947">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2947">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2976">Skatteidentifieringsnummer för Cypern</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2976">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2977">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2977">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2978">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2978">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2979">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2979">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2980">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2980">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2981">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2981">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2982">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2982">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2983">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2984">Åtta siffror och en bokstav i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2984">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2985">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2986">Åtta siffror och en bokstav:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2986">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2987">a "0" eller "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2987">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2988">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2988">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2989">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2989">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2990">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2990">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2991">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2991">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2992">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2992">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2993">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2993">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2994">Funktionen hittar  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2994">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2995">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2995">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2996">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2996">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2997">Funktionen hittar  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2997">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2998">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2998">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-2999">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-2999">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3000">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3000">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3001">tax identification code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3001">tax identification code</span></span>

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3025">Tjeckiska körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3025">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3026">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3026">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3027">Två bokstäver följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3027">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3028">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3028">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3029">Åtta bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3029">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3030">bokstaven "E" (inte den är det.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3030">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3031">en bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3031">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3032">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3032">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3033">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3033">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3034">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3034">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3035">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3035">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3036">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3036">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3037">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3037">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3038">Det reguljära  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3038">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3039">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3039">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3165">Tjeckiska passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3165">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3166">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3166">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3167">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3167">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3168">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3168">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3169">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3169">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3170">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3170">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3171">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3171">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3172">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3172">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3173">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3173">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3174">Det reguljära  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3174">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3175">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3175">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3176">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3176">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3177">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3177">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3178">Det reguljära  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3178">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3179">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3179">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3201">Tjeckiska personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3201">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3202">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3203">Nio siffror med valfritt snedstreck (gammalt format) 10 siffror med valfritt snedstreck (nytt format)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3203">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3204">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3204">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3205">Nio siffror (gammalt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3205">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3206">Sex siffror som representerar födelsedatum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3206">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3207">ett valfritt snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3207">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3208">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3208">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3209">10 siffror (nytt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3209">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3210">Sex siffror som representerar födelsedatum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3210">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3211">ett valfritt snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3211">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3212">fyra siffror där sista siffran är en bård</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3212">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3213">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3213">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3214">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3214">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3215">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3215">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3216">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3216">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3217">Funktionen för Func_czech_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3217">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3218">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_czech_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3218">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3219">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3219">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3220">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3220">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3221">Funktionen Func_czech_id_card_new_format hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3221">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3222">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3222">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3269">Danmarks körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3269">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3270">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3270">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3271">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3271">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3272">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3272">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3273">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3273">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3274">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3275">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3275">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3276">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3277">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3277">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3278">Det reguljära  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3278">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3279">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3279">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3403">Danmark passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3403">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3404">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3405">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3405">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3406">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3407">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3407">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3408">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3408">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3409">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3409">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3410">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3410">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3411">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3411">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3412">Det reguljära  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3412">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3413">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3413">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3414">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date2` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD MM YY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3414">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3415">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3415">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3416">Det reguljära  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3416">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3417">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3417">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3437">Danmarks personliga ID-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3437">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3438">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3438">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3439">10 siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3439">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3440">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3440">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3441">10 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3441">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3442">Sex siffror i formatet DDMMYY, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3442">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3443">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3443">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3444">fyra siffror där den sista siffran är en bård</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3444">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3445">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3445">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3446">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3446">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3447">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3447">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3448">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3448">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3449">Det reguljära uttrycket Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3449">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3450">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_denmark_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3450">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3451">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3451">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3452">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3452">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3453">Det reguljära uttrycket Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3453">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3454">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3454">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3526">Dea-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3526">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3527">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3527">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3528">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3528">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3529">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3529">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3530">Mönster måste omfatta alla följande:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3530">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3531">en bokstav (inte den här uppsättning möjliga bokstäver) från den här uppsättningen möjliga bokstäver: abcdefghjklmnprstux, som är en registrantkod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3531">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3532">en bokstav (inte fallkänslig), som är den första bokstaven i registrantens efternamn eller siffran "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3532">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3533">sju siffror, den sista är bårdsiffran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3533">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3534">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3534">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3535">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3535">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3536">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3536">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3537">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3537">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3538">Funktionen Func_dea_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3538">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3539">Ett nyckelord `Keyword_dea_number` från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3539">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3540">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3540">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3541">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3541">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3542">Funktionen Func_dea_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3542">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3543">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3543">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3545">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3545">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3550">Estlands körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3550">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3551">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3552">Två bokstäver följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3552">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3553">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3554">Två bokstäver och sex siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3554">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3555">bokstäverna "ET" (inte case-sensitive)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3555">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3556">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3556">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3557">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3557">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3558">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3558">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3559">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3559">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3560">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3560">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3561">Det reguljära  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3561">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3562">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3562">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3563">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3563">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3565">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3565">driverlic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3690">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3690">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3696">11 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3696">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3697">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3698">11 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3698">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3699">en siffra som motsvarar sex och ett sekel (udda nummer man, jämn kvinna; 1–2: 19:e talet; 3–4: 20:e talet; 5–6: 2000)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3699">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3700">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (DSMMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3700">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3701">Tre siffror som motsvarar ett serienummer som separerar personer som föds samma datum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3701">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3702">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3702">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3703">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3704">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3704">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3705">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3706">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3706">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3707">Funktionen hittar  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3707">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3708">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3708">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3709">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3709">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3710">Funktionen hittar  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3710">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
