## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3743">Estland passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3743">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3744">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3745">en bokstav följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3745">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3746">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3747">en bokstav följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3747">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3748">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3748">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3749">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3749">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3750">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3750">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3751">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3751">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3752">Det reguljära  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3752">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3753">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3753">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3754">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3754">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3755">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3755">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3756">Det reguljära  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3756">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3757">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3757">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3775">BETALKORTSNUMMER (EU)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3775">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3776">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3776">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3777">16 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3777">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3778">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3778">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3779">Komplext och robust mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3779">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3780">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3780">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3781">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3781">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3782">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3782">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3783">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3783">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3784">Funktionen för Func_eu_debit_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3784">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3785">Minst ett av följande stämmer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3785">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3786">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_eu_debit_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3786">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3787">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_card_terms_dict hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3787">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3788">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_card_security_terms_dict hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3788">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3789">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3789">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3790">Funktionen Func_expiration_date hittar ett datum i rätt datumformat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3790">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3791">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3791">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3792">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3792">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_eu_debit_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-3793">Keyword_eu_debit_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-3793">Keyword_eu_debit_card</span></span>

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4238">Finlands körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4238">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4239">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4239">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4240">10 siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4240">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4241">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4241">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4242">10 siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4242">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4243">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4243">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4244">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4244">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4245">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4245">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4246">en siffra eller bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4246">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4247">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4248">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4248">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4249">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4250">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4250">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4251">Det reguljära  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4251">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4252">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4252">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4383">Finlands hälsoförsäkringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4383">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4384">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4384">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4385">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4385">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4386">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4386">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4387">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4387">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4388">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4388">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4389">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4389">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4390">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4390">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4391">20-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4391">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4392">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4392">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4393">20-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4393">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4394">10 siffror – 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4394">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4395">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4395">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4396">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4396">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4397">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4397">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4398">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4398">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4399">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4399">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4400">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4400">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4401">Regex-Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4401">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4402">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4402">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4420">Finlands national-ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4420">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4421">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4421">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4422">Sex siffror plus ett tecken som anger ett sekel plus tre siffror plus en bård</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4422">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4423">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4423">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4424">Mönster måste omfatta alla följande:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4424">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4425">Sex siffror i formatet DDMMYY, som är ett födelsedatum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4425">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4426">talmarkör (antingen '-', '+' eller 'a')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4426">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4427">tresiffrigt id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4427">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4428">En siffra eller bokstav (tecken insensitiv) som är en kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4428">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4429">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4429">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4430">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4430">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4431">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4431">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4432">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4432">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4433">funktionen som Func_finnish_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4433">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4434">ett nyckelord från Keyword_finnish_national_id hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4434">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4435">kontrollsumma passeras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4435">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4436">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4436">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4437">funktionen som Func_finnish_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4437">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4438">kontrollsumma passeras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4438">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4487">Finland passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4487">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4488">Den här typen av känslig information är tillgänglig i typen KÄNSLIG informationstyp EU Passport Number och är tillgänglig som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4488">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4489">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4489">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4490">kombination av nio bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4490">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4491">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4491">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4492">kombination av nio bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4492">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4493">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4493">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4494">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4494">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4495">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4495">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4496">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4496">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4497">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4497">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4498">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4498">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4499">Det reguljära `Regex_finland_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4499">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4500">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_finland_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4500">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4501">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4501">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4502">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4502">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4503">Det reguljära `Regex_finland_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4503">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4504">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_finland_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4504">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4505">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4505">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4506">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4506">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4507">pass #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4507">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4508">pass #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4508">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4509">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4509">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4510">pass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4510">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4511">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4511">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4512">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4512">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4528">Frankrikes körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4528">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4529">Den här typen av känslig information är tillgänglig i EU-drivrutinens licensnummerkänsliga informationstyp och är tillgänglig som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4529">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4530">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4530">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4531">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4531">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4532">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4532">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4533">12 siffror med validering för rabatt på liknande mönster som franska telefonnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4533">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4534">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4534">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4535">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4535">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4536">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4536">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4537">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4537">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4538">funktionen Func_french_drivers_license hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4538">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4539">ett nyckelord från Keyword_french_drivers_license hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4539">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4667">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4667">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4668">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4668">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4670">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4670">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4671">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4671">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4672">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4672">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4673">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4673">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4675">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4675">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4676">21-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4676">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4677">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4677">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4678">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4678">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4679">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4679">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4680">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4680">an optional space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4682">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4682">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4683">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4683">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4684">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4684">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4685">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4685">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4686">regex-Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4686">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4687">ett nyckelord från Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4687">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4693">France national id card (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4693">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4694">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4694">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4695">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4695">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4696">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4696">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4697">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4697">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4698">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4698">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4699">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4699">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4700">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4700">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4701">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4701">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4702">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_france_cni hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4702">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4703">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4703">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4717">Frankrike passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4717">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4718">Den här typen av känslig information är tillgänglig i typen Känslig information av EU-passnummer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4718">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4719">Det är tillgängligt som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4719">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4720">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4720">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4721">Nio siffror och bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4721">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4722">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4722">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4723">Nio siffror och bokstäver:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4723">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4724">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4724">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4725">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4725">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4726">fem siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4726">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4727">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4728">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4728">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4729">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4730">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4730">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4731">Funktionen hittar `Func_fr_passport` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4731">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4732">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4732">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4733">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date3` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD MM YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4733">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4734">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4734">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4735">Funktionen hittar `Func_fr_passport` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4735">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4736">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4736">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4737">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4737">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4738">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4738">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4739">pass #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4739">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4740">pass #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4740">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4741">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4741">passportid</span></span>

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4767">Frankrikes personnummer (INSEE)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4767">France social security number (INSEE)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4768">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4768">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4769">15 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4769">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4770">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4770">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4771">Måste matcha ett av två mönster:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4771">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4772">13 siffror följt av ett blanksteg följt av två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4772">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4773">eller</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4773">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4774">15 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4774">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4775">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4776">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4776">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4777">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4778">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4778">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4779">Funktionen hittar `Func_french_insee` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4779">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4780">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_fr_insee hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4780">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4781">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4781">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4782">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4782">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4783">Funktionen Func_french_insee eller Func_fr_insee hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4783">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4784">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4784">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4815">Frankrikes skattenummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4815">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4816">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4816">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4817">13 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4817">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4818">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4818">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4819">13 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4819">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4820">En siffra som måste vara 0, 1, 2 eller 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4820">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4821">En siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4821">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4822">Ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4822">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4823">Två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4823">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4824">Ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4824">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4825">Tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4825">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4826">Ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4826">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4827">Tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4827">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4828">Ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4828">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4829">Tre kontrollsiffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4829">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4830">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4830">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4831">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4831">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4832">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4832">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4833">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4833">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4834">Funktionen hittar  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4834">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4835">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4835">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4836">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4836">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4837">Funktionen hittar  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4837">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4857">Värdeskattenummer för Frankrike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4857">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4858">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4858">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4859">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4859">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4860">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4860">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4861">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4861">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4862">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4862">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4863">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4863">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4865">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 13 tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4865">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4866">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4867">13 tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4867">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4868">två bokstäver – FR (teckenkänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4868">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4869">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4869">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4870">två bokstäver eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4870">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4871">Ett valfritt blanksteg, punkt, bindestreck eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4871">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4872">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4872">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4873">Ett valfritt blanksteg, punkt, bindestreck eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4873">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4874">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4874">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4875">Ett valfritt blanksteg, punkt, bindestreck eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4875">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4876">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4876">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4877">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4877">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4878">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4878">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4879">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4879">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4880">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4880">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4881">Funktionen för Func_france_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4881">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4882">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4882">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4883">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4883">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4884">Funktionen för Func_france_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4884">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4897">Tysklands körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4897">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4898">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i EU:s typ av licensnummer för känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4898">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4899">Det är tillgängligt som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4899">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4900">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4900">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4901">kombination av 11 siffror och bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4901">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4902">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4902">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4903">11 siffror och bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4903">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4904">en siffra eller bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4904">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4905">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4905">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4906">Sex siffror eller bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4906">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4907">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4907">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4908">en siffra eller bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4908">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4909">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4910">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4910">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4911">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4912">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4912">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4913">Funktionen för Func_german_drivers_license hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4913">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4914">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_german_drivers_license_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4914">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-4915">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-4915">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5064">Identitetskortsnummer i Tyskland</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5064">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5065">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5065">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5066">sedan 1 november 2010: nio bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5066">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5067">från 1 april 1987 till 31 oktober 2010: 10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5067">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5068">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5068">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5069">sedan 1 november 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5069">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5070">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5070">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5071">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5071">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5072">från den 1 april 1987 till den 31 oktober 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5072">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5073">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5073">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5074">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5075">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5075">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5076">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5077">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5077">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5078">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_germany_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5078">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5079">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_germany_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5079">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5080">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5080">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5095">Tyskland passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5095">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5096">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i typen Känslig information i EU Passport Number och är tillgänglig som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5096">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5097">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5097">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5098">10 siffror eller bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5098">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5099">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5099">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5100">Mönster måste omfatta alla följande:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5100">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5101">det första tecknet är en siffra eller en bokstav från denna uppsättning (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5101">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5102">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5102">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5103">Fem siffror eller bokstäver från denna uppsättning (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5103">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5104">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5104">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5105">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5105">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5106">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5106">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5107">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5107">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5108">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5108">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5109">Funktionen för Func_german_passport hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5109">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5110">Ett nyckelord från `Keyword_german_passport` eller `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5110">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5111">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5111">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5112">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5112">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5113">Funktionen för Func_german_passport_data hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5113">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5114">Ett nyckelord från `Keyword_german_passport` eller `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5114">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5115">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5115">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5138">Tysklands skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5138">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5139">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5139">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5140">11 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5140">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5141">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5141">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5142">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5142">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5143">Två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5143">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5144">Ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5144">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5145">Tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5145">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5146">Ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5146">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5147">Tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5147">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5148">Ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5148">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5149">Två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5149">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5150">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5150">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5151">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5152">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5152">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5153">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5154">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5154">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5155">Funktionen hittar  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5155">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5156">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5156">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5157">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5157">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5158">Funktionen hittar  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5158">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5184">Momsnummer för Tyskland</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5184">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5185">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5185">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5186">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5186">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5187">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5187">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5188">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5188">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5189">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5189">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5190">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5190">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5191">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5191">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5192">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 11 tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5192">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5193">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5193">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5194">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 11 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5194">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5195">a bokstaven D eller d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5195">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5196">ett bokstaven E eller e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5196">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5197">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5197">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5198">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5198">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5199">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5199">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5200">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5200">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5201">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5201">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5202">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5202">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5203">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5203">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5204">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5204">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5205">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5205">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5206">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5206">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5207">Funktionen för Func_germany_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5207">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5208">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5208">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5209">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5209">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5210">Funktionen för Func_germany_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5210">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
