## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5220">Greklands körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5220">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5221">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i EU-drivrutinens typ av licensnummerkänslig information och är tillgänglig som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5221">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5222">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5222">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5223">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5223">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5224">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5224">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5225">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5225">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5226">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5226">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5227">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5227">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5228">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5228">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5229">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5229">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5230">Det reguljära  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5230">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5231">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5231">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5357">Greklands nationella ID-kort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5357">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5358">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5358">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5359">Kombination av 7–8 bokstäver och siffror plus ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5359">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5360">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5360">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5361">Sju bokstäver och siffror (gammalt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5361">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5362">En bokstav (valfri bokstav i det grekiska alfabetet)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5362">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5363">Ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5363">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5364">Sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5364">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5365">Åtta bokstäver och siffror (nytt format):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5365">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5366">Två bokstäver med versaler både i det grekiska och det latinska alfabetet (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5366">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5367">Ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5367">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5368">Sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5368">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5369">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5369">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5370">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5370">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5371">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5371">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5372">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5372">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5373">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_greece_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5373">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5374">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_greece_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5374">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5375">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5375">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5376">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_greece_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5376">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5381">grekiska personliga ID-kort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5381">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5382">grekiska police id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5382">greek police id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5385">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5385">ταυτότητα</span></span>

## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5387">Greklands passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5387">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5388">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5388">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5389">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5389">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5390">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5390">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5391">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5391">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5392">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5392">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5393">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5393">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5394">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5394">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5395">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5395">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5396">Det reguljära  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5396">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5397">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5397">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5398">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` formatet DD MMM YY (Exempel - 28 augusti 19) eller ett `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` nyckelord från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5398">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5399">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5399">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5400">Det reguljära  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5400">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5401">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5401">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5414">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5414">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5415">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5415">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5416">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5416">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5417">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5417">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5418">Greklands social securitynummer (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5418">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5419">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5419">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5420">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5420">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5421">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5421">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5422">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5422">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5423">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5423">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5424">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5424">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5425">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5425">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5426">Elva siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5426">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5427">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5427">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5428">6 siffror som födelsedatum YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5428">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5429">4 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5429">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5430">en kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5430">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5431">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5431">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5432">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5432">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5433">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5433">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5434">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5434">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5435">Funktionen hittar  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5435">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5436">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5436">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5437">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5437">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5438">Funktionen hittar  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5438">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5450">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5450">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5451">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5451">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5455">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5455">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5456">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5456">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5457">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5457">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5458">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5458">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5459">Nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5459">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5460">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5460">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5461">Ej tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5461">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5462">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5462">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5463">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5463">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5464">Det reguljära  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5464">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5465">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5465">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5494">Hongkong identitetskort (HKID) nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5494">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5495">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5495">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5496">Kombination av 8–9 bokstäver och siffror samt valfria parenteser runt det sista tecknet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5496">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5497">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5497">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5498">Kombination av 8–9 bokstäver:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5498">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5499">1–2 bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5499">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5500">Sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5500">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5501">Det sista tecknet (valfri siffra eller bokstaven A), som är en kontrollsiffra och som kan omges av parenteser.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5501">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5502">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5502">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5503">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5503">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5504">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5504">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5505">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5505">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5506">Funktionen för Func_hong_kong_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5506">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5507">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_hong_kong_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5507">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5508">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5508">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5509">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5509">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5510">Funktionen för Func_hong_kong_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5510">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5511">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5511">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5512">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5512">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hong_kong_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5513">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5513">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5514">hkid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5514">hkid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5515">Hong Kong-identitetskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5515">hong kong identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5516">HKIDC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5516">HKIDC</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5551">Ungerns körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5551">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5552">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5552">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5553">Två bokstäver följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5553">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5554">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5554">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5555">Två bokstäver och sex siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5555">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5556">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5556">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5557">Sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5557">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5558">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5558">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5559">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5559">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5560">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5560">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5561">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5561">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5562">Det reguljära  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5562">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5563">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5563">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5688">Ungerns personliga ID-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5688">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5689">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5689">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5690">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5690">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5691">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5691">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5692">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5692">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5693">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5693">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5694">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5694">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5696">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5696">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5697">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5698">11 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5698">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5699">En siffra som motsvarar kön (1-man, 2-kvinna, andra siffror är också möjliga för människor som föddes före 1900 eller för att människor med dubbel kön)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5699">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5700">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatum (AMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5700">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5701">Tre siffror som motsvarar ett serienummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5701">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5702">En kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5702">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5703">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5704">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5704">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5705">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5706">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5706">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5707">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5707">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5708">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5708">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5709">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5709">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5710">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5710">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5711">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5711">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5713">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5713">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5714">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5714">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5715">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5715">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5716">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5716">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5717">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5717">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5718">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5718">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5719">személyazonosító igamévány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5719">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5720">személyi igaávány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5720">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5721">Ungern passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5721">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5722">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5723">Två bokstäver följt av sex eller sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5723">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5724">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5725">Två bokstäver följt av sex eller sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5725">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5726">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5727">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5727">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5728">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5729">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5730">Det reguljära  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5730">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5731">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5731">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5732">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` formatet DD MMM/MMM YY (Exempel - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5732">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5733">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5733">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5734">Det reguljära  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5734">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5735">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5735">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5755">Ungerns social security number (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5755">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5756">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5757">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5757">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5758">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5759">Nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5759">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5760">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5760">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5761">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5761">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5762">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5762">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5763">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5763">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5764">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5764">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5765">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5765">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5766">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5767">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5767">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5787">Ungerns skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5787">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5788">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5788">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5789">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5789">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5790">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5790">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5791">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5791">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5792">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5792">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5793">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5793">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5794">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5795">10 siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5795">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5796">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5797">10 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5797">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5798">En siffra som måste vara "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5798">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5799">Åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5799">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5800">En kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5800">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5801">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5802">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5802">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5803">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5804">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5804">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5805">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5805">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5806">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5806">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5807">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5808">Funktionen hittar  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5808">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5843">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5843">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5844">10 tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5844">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5845">två bokstäver – HU eller hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5845">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5846">valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5846">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5847">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5847">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5848">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5848">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5849">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5849">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5850">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5850">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5851">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5851">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5852">Funktionen Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5852">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5853">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5853">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5854">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5854">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5855">Funktionen Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5855">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5858">moms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5858">vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5859">momsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5859">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5860">moms #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5860">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5861">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5861">vatno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5868">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5868">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5869">Indiens permanenta kontonummer (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5869">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5870">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5870">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5871">10 bokstäver eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5871">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5872">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5872">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5873">10 bokstäver eller siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5873">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5874">Tre bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5874">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5875">En bokstav i C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (inte ärendekänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5875">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5876">En bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5876">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5877">Fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5877">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5878">En bokstav med en alfabetisk kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5878">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5879">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5879">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5880">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5880">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5881">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5881">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5882">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5882">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5883">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_india_permanent_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5883">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5884">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_india_permanent_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5884">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5885">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5885">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5886">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_india_permanent_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5886">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5887">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5887">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5889">Permanent kontonummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5889">Permanent Account Number</span></span>

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5891">Indiens unika ID-nummer (Aadhaar)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5891">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5892">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5892">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5893">12 siffror som innehåller valfria blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5893">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5894">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5894">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5895">12 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5895">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5896">En siffra som inte är 0 eller 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5896">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5897">Tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5897">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5898">Ett blanksteg eller streck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5898">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5899">Fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5899">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5900">Ett blanksteg eller streck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5900">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5901">Den sista siffran, som är kontrollsiffran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5901">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5902">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5902">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5903">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5903">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5904">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5904">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5905">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5905">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5906">Funktionen för Func_india_aadhaar hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5906">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5907">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_india_aadhar hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5907">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5908">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5908">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5909">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5910">Funktionen för Func_india_aadhaar hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5910">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5911">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5911">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5917">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5917">uid</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5920">Indonesia Identity Card-nummer (KTP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5920">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5921">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5922">16 siffror med valfria punkter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5922">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5923">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5924">16 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5924">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5925">Tvåsiffrig provinskod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5925">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5926">En punkt (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5926">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5927">Tvåsiffrig regency eller ortkod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5927">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5928">Tvåsiffrig underpriskod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5928">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5929">En punkt (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5929">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5930">Sex siffror i formatet DDMMYY, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5930">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5931">En punkt (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5931">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5932">Fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5932">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5933">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5933">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5934">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5934">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5935">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5935">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5936">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5936">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5937">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_indonesia_id_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5937">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5938">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_indonesia_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5938">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5939">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5939">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5944">Nummer för internationella banktjänster (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5944">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5945">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5945">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5946">Landskod (två bokstäver) plus kontrollera siffror (två siffror) plus bban-nummer (upp till 30 tecken)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5946">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5947">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5947">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5948">Mönster måste omfatta alla följande:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5948">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5949">Landskod med två bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5949">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5950">Två kontrollsiffror (följt av ett valfritt blanksteg)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5950">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5951">1–7 grupper med fyra bokstäver eller siffror (kan avgränsas med blanksteg)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5951">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5952">1–3 bokstäver eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5952">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5953">Formatet skiljer sig åt mellan olika länder.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5953">The format for each country is slightly different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5954">IBAN-typen för känslig information omfattar dessa 60 länder:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5954">The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5955">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, jan, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5955">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5956">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5956">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5957">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5957">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5958">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5958">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5959">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5959">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5960">Funktionen Func_iban hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5960">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5961">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5961">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5965">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5965">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5966">Ordlista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5966">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5967">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5967">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5968">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5968">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5969">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5969">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5970">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5970">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5971">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5971">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5972">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5972">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5973">Ett nyckelord från Dictionary_icd_10_updated hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5973">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5974">Ett nyckelord från Dictionary_icd_10_codes hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5974">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5975">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5975">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5976">Ett nyckelord från Dictionary_icd_10_ har uppdaterats hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5976">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5977">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5977">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5978">Valfri term från nyckelordsordlistan i Dictionary_icd_10_updated, som baseras på den internationella klassificeringen av den internationella klassificeringen, den tionde revisionen, den kliniskt [modifieringen (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5978">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5979">Den här typen söker bara efter termen, inte för försäkringskoderna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5979">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5980">Valfri term från nyckelordsordlistan i Dictionary_icd_10_codes, som baseras på den internationella klassificeringen av ärevisionen, tionde revision, klinisk ändring [(ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5980">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5981">Den här typen söker bara efter försäkringskoder, inte beskrivningen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5981">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5996">Valfri term från nyckelordsordlistan i Dictionary_icd_9_updated, som baseras på den internationella klassificeringen av det här ordet, den nionde revisionen, den kliniskt [modifieringen (ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5996">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-5997">Den här typen söker bara efter termen, inte för försäkringskoderna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-5997">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>
