## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6000">IP-adress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6000">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6001">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6001">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6002">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6002">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6003">Komplext mönster som konton för formaterade (punkter) och oformaterade (inga perioder) versioner av IPv4-adresser</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6003">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6004">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6004">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6005">Komplext mönster som står för formaterade IPv6-tal (som innehåller kolon)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6005">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6006">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6006">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6007">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6007">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6008">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6008">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6009">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6009">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6010">För IPv6 har en DLP-princip med hög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6010">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6011">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_ipv6_address hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6011">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6012">Inget nyckelord från Keyword_ipaddress hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6012">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6013">För IPv4 har en DLP-princip med hög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6013">For IPv4, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6014">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_ipv4_address hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6014">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6015">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ipaddress hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6015">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6016">För IPv6 har en DLP-princip med hög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6016">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6017">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_ipv6_address hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6017">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6018">Inget nyckelord från Keyword_ipaddress hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6018">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6025">IP-כתובת</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6025">IP-כתובת ה</span></span> 

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6026">Irlands körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6026">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6027">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6027">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6028">Sex siffror följt av fyra bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6028">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6029">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6029">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6030">Sex siffror och fyra bokstäver:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6030">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6031">Sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6031">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6032">Fyra bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6032">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6033">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6033">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6034">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6034">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6035">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6035">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6036">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6036">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6037">Det reguljära  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6037">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6038">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6038">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6162">Irland, passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6162">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6163">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6164">Två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6164">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6165">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6166">Två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6166">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6167">Två siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6167">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6168">Sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6168">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6169">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6170">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6171">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6172">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6172">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6173">Det reguljära  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6173">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6174">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6174">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6175">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i formatet `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Exempel - 01 BEA/MAJ 1988) eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6175">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6176">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6176">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6177">Det reguljära  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6177">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6178">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6178">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6202">PpS-nummer (Personal Public Service) för Irland</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6202">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6203">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6203">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6204">Gammalt format (till 31 december 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6204">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6205">sju siffror följt av 1–2 bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6205">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6206">Nytt format (1 januari 2013 och senare):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6206">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6207">sju siffror följt av två bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6207">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6208">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6208">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6209">Gammalt format (till 31 december 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6209">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6210">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6210">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6211">En till två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6211">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6212">Nytt format (1 januari 2013 och senare):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6212">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6213">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6213">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6214">En bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig) som är en alfabetisk kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6214">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6215">En valfri bokstav i cellområdet A-I eller "W"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6215">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6216">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6216">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6217">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6217">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6218">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6218">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6219">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6219">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6220">Funktionen för Func_ireland_pps hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6220">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6221">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6221">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6222">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6222">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6223">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6223">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6224">Funktionen för Func_ireland_pps hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6224">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6225">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6225">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6270">Bankkontonummer för Israel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6270">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6271">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6272">13 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6272">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6273">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6274">Formaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6274">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6275">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6275">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6276">ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6276">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6277">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6277">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6278">ett streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6278">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6279">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6279">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6280">Oformaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6280">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6281">13 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6281">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6282">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6282">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6283">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6283">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6284">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6284">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6285">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6285">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6286">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_israel_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6286">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6287">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_israel_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6287">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6294">Israels national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6294">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6295">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6295">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6296">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6296">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6297">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6297">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6298">nio siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6298">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6299">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6299">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6300">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6300">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6301">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6301">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6302">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6302">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6303">Funktionen för Func_israeli_national_id_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6303">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6304">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Israel_National_ID hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6304">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6305">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6305">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6324">Italiens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6324">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6325">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i EU-drivrutinens typ av licensnummerkänslig information och är tillgänglig som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6325">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6326">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6326">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6327">en kombination av 10 bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6327">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6328">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6328">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6329">en kombination av 10 bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6329">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6330">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6330">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6331">bokstaven "A" eller "V" (inte ärendekänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6331">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6332">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6332">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6333">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6333">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6334">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6334">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6335">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6335">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6336">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6336">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6337">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6337">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6338">Det reguljära `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6338">The regular expression `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6339">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6339">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
    <Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6466">Italiens räkenskapskod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6466">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6467">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6467">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6468">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6468">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6469">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6469">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6470">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6470">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6471">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6471">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6472">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6472">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6473">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6474">En kombination av bokstäver och siffror på 16 tecken i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6474">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6475">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6476">En kombination av 16 tecken och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6476">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6477">Tre bokstäver som motsvarar de tre första konsonanterna i familjenamnet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6477">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6478">Tre bokstäver som motsvarar den första, tredje och fjärde konsonanterna i förnamnet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6478">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6479">två siffror som motsvarar de sista siffrorna i födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6479">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6480">en bokstav som motsvarar bokstaven för födelsedatumet – bokstäver används i alfabetisk ordning, men bara bokstäverna A till E, H, L, M, P, R till T används (så januari är A och oktober är R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6480">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6481">Två siffror som motsvarar dagen i månaden – för att skilja på kön läggs 40 till för kvinnor</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6481">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6482">fyra siffror som motsvarar den specifika areakoden för den valuta som personen är föds på (landskoder används för externa länder)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6482">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6483">en paritetssiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6483">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6484">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6484">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6485">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6485">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6486">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6486">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6487">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6487">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6488">Funktionen hittar  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6488">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6489">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6489">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6490">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6490">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6491">Funktionen hittar  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6491">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6526">Italien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6526">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6527">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6527">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6528">två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6528">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6529">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6529">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6530">Två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6530">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6531">två siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6531">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6532">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6532">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6533">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6533">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6534">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6534">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6535">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6535">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6536">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6536">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6537">Det reguljära  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6537">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6538">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6538">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6539">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i formatet `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Exempel - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6539">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6540">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6540">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6541">Det reguljära  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6541">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6542">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6542">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6566">Momsnummer i Italien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6566">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6567">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6567">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6568">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6568">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6569">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6569">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6570">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6570">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6571">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6571">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6572">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6572">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6573">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6573">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6574">13 tecken för alfanumeriska mönster med valfria avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6574">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6575">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6575">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6576">13 tecken med alfanumeriska mönster med valfria avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6576">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6577">I eller i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6577">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6578">T eller t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6578">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6579">Valfritt blanksteg, punkt, bindestreck eller kommatecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6579">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6580">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6580">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6581">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6581">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6582">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6582">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6583">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6583">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6584">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6584">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6585">Funktionen Func_italy_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6585">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6586">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6586">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6587">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6587">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6588">Funktionen Func_italy_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6588">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6596">Bankkontonummer för Japan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6596">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6597">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6597">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6598">sju eller åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6598">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6599">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6599">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6600">bankkontonummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6600">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6601">sju eller åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6601">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6602">bankkontokontorskod:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6602">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6603">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6603">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6604">Blanksteg eller streck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6604">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6605">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6605">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6606">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6607">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6608">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6609">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6609">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6610">Funktionen Func_jp_bank_account hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6610">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6611">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_bank_account hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6611">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6612">Något av följande är sant:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6612">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6613">Funktionen för Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6613">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6614">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6614">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6615">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6615">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6616">Funktionen Func_jp_bank_account hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6616">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6617">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_bank_account hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6617">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6665">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6665">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6666">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6666">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6667">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6667">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6668">12 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6668">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6669">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6669">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6670">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6670">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6671">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6671">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6672">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6672">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6673">Funktionen Func_jp_drivers_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6673">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6674">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6674">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6712">Japan, mitt nummer – företag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6712">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6713">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6713">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6714">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6714">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6715">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6715">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6716">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6716">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6717">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6717">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6718">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6718">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6719">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6719">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6720">13-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6720">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6721">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6721">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6722">13-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6722">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6723">en siffra från en till nio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6723">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6724">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6724">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6725">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6725">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6726">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6726">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6727">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6727">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6728">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6728">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6729">Funktionen Func_japanese_my_number_corporate hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6729">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6730">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6730">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6731">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6731">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6732">Funktionen Func_japanese_my_number_corporate hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6732">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6740">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6740">個人番号カード</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6746">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6746">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6747">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6747">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6748">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6748">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6749">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6749">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6750">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6750">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6751">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6751">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6752">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6752">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6753">12-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6753">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6754">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6754">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6755">12-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6755">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6756">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6756">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6757">Ett valfritt blanksteg, punkt eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6757">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6758">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6758">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6759">Ett valfritt blanksteg, punkt eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6759">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6760">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6760">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6761">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6762">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6762">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6763">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6764">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6764">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6765">Funktionen för Func_japanese_my_number_personal hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6765">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6766">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6766">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6767">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6767">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6768">Funktionen för Func_japanese_my_number_personal hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6768">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6781">Japan passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6781">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6782">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6782">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6783">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6783">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6784">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6784">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6785">Två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga) följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6785">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6786">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6786">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6787">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6787">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6788">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6788">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6789">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6789">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6790">Funktionen för Func_jp_passport hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6790">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6791">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_passport hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6791">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6792">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6792">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6808">Japan residence card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6808">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6809">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6809">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6810">12 bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6810">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6811">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6811">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6812">12 bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6812">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6813">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6813">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6814">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6814">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6815">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6815">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6816">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6816">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6817">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6817">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6818">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6818">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6819">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6819">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6820">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_jp_residence_card_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6820">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6821">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_residence_card_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6821">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6822">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6822">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6823">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6823">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6824">Residence card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6824">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6825">Residence card no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6825">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6826">Residence card #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6826">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6827">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6827">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6828">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6828">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6829">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6829">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6830">Registreringsnummer för boende i Japan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6830">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6831">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6831">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6832">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6832">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6833">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6833">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6834">11 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6834">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6835">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6835">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6836">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6836">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6837">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6837">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6838">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6838">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6839">Funktionen för Func_jp_resident_registration_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6839">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6840">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6840">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6853">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6853">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6854">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6854">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6855">7-12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6855">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6856">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6856">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6857">7-12 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6857">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6858">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6858">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6859">Ett bindestreck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6859">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6860">sex siffror ELLER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6860">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6861">7–12 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6861">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6862">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6862">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6863">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6863">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6864">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6864">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6865">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6865">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6866">Funktionen för Func_jp_sin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6866">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6867">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_sin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6867">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6868">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6868">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6869">Funktionen för Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6869">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6870">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_jp_sin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6870">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6891">Lettiska körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6891">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6892">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6892">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6893">Tre bokstäver följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6893">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6894">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6894">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6895">tre bokstäver och sex siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6895">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6896">Tre bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6896">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6897">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6897">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6898">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6898">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6899">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6899">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6900">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6900">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6901">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6901">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6902">Det reguljära  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6902">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-6903">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-6903">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
