## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7028">Personlig kod för Lettland</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7028">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7029">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7029">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7030">11 siffror och ett valfritt bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7030">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7031">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7031">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7032">Gammalt format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7032">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7033">11 siffror och ett bindestreck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7033">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7034">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7034">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7035">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7035">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7036">en siffra som motsvarar födelsedatumet ("0" för 19:e talet, "1" för 20:e talet och "2" för 2000-talet)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7036">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7037">fyra siffror, slumpmässigt genererade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7037">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7038">Nytt format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7038">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7039">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7039">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7040">Två siffror "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7040">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7041">Nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7041">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7042">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7042">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7043">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7043">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7044">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7044">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7045">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7045">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7046">Funktionen eller  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex hittar `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7046">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7047">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7047">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7048">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7048">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7049">Funktionen eller  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex hittar `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7049">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7112">Lettiska passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7112">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7113">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7113">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7114">två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7114">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7115">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7115">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7116">Två bokstäver eller siffror följt av sju siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7116">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7117">två siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7117">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7118">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7118">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7119">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7119">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7120">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7120">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7121">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7122">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7122">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7123">Det reguljära  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7123">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7124">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7124">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7125">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7125">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7126">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7126">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7127">Det reguljära  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7127">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7128">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7128">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7151">Litauens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7151">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7152">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7152">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7153">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7153">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7154">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7154">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7155">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7155">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7156">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7156">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7157">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7157">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7158">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7158">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7159">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7159">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7160">Det reguljära  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7160">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7161">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7161">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7286">Personlig kod för Litauen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7286">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7287">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7287">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7288">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7288">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7289">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7289">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7290">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7290">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7291">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7291">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7292">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7292">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7293">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7293">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7294">11 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7294">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7295">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7295">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7296">11 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7296">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7297">en siffra (1–6) som motsvarar personens kön och födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7297">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7298">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatum (AMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7298">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7299">Tre siffror som motsvarar serienumret för födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7299">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7300">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7300">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7301">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7301">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7302">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7302">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7303">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7303">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7304">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7304">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7305">Funktionen hittar  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7305">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7306">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7306">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7307">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7307">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7308">Funktionen hittar  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7308">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7343">Litauen passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7343">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7344">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7344">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7345">åtta siffror eller bokstäver utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7345">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7346">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7346">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7347">åtta siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7347">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7348">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7348">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7349">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7349">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7350">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7350">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7351">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7351">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7352">Det reguljära  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7352">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7353">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7353">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7354">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date3` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD MM YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7354">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7355">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7355">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7356">Det reguljära  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7356">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7357">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7357">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7378">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7379">Sex siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7379">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7380">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7380">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7382">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7383">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7383">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7384">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7385">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7385">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7386">Det reguljära  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7386">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7387">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7387">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7511">Luxemburgs national identification number (natural persons)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7511">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7512">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7512">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7513">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7513">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7514">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7514">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7515">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7515">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7516">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7516">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7517">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7517">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7518">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7518">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7519">13 siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7519">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7520">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7520">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7521">13 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7521">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7522">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7522">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7523">två kontrollsiffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7523">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7524">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7524">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7525">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7525">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7526">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7526">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7527">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7527">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7528">Funktionen hittar  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7528">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7529">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7529">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7530">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7530">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7531">Funktionen hittar  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7531">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7554">Luxemburg-passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7554">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7555">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7555">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7556">åtta siffror eller bokstäver utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7556">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7557">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7557">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7558">åtta siffror eller bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7558">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7559">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7559">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7560">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7560">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7561">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7561">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7562">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7562">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7563">Det reguljära  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7563">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7564">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7564">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7565">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date3` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD MM YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7565">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7566">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7566">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7567">Det reguljära  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7567">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7568">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7568">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7600">Luxemburgs national identification number (icke-naturliga personer)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7600">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7601">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7602">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7602">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7603">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7604">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7604">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7605">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7605">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7606">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7606">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7607">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7607">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7608">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7608">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7609">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7609">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7610">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7610">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7611">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7611">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7612">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7612">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7613">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7613">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7614">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7614">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7615">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7615">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7616">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7616">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7617">Funktionen hittar  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7617">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7618">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7618">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7619">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7619">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7620">Funktionen hittar  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7620">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7660">Malaysia identification card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7660">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7661">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7661">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7662">12 siffror med valfria bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7662">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7663">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7663">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7664">12 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7664">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7665">Sex siffror i formatet YYMMDD, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7665">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7666">Ett streck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7666">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7667">plats-av-födelsedatum med två bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7667">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7668">Ett streck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7668">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7669">tre slumpmässiga siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7669">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7670">ensiffrig kön-kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7670">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7671">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7672">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7672">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7673">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7674">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7674">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7675">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_malaysia_id_card_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7675">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7676">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7676">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7677">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7677">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7685">identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7685">identification Card</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7703">Maltas körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7703">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7704">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7704">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7705">Kombination av två tecken och sex siffror i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7705">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7706">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7706">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7707">kombination av två tecken och sex siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7707">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7708">Två tecken (siffror eller bokstäver, inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7708">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7709">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7709">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7710">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7710">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7711">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7711">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7712">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7712">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7713">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7713">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7714">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7714">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7715">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7715">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7716">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7716">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7717">Det reguljära  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7717">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7718">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7718">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7842">Malta-identitetskortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7842">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7843">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7843">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7844">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7844">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7845">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7845">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7846">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7846">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7847">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7847">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7848">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7848">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7849">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7849">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7850">sju siffror följt av en bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7850">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7851">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7851">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7852">sju siffror följt av en bokstav:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7852">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7853">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7853">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7854">en bokstav i "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (ärendekänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7854">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7855">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7855">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7856">Ej tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7856">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7857">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7857">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7858">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7858">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7859">Det reguljära  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7859">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7860">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7860">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7861">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7861">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7862">Det reguljära  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7862">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7879">Malta passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7879">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7880">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7880">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7881">sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7881">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7882">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7882">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7883">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7883">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7884">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7884">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7885">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7885">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7886">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7886">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7887">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7887">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7888">Det reguljära  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7888">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7889">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7889">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7890">Ett nyckelord `Keywords_eu_passport_date` från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7890">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7891">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7891">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7892">Det reguljära  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7892">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7893">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7893">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7913">Maltas skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7913">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7914">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7915">För Maltesiska:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7915">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7916">sju siffror och en bokstav i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7916">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7917">Non-Denesiska ochesiska enheter:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7917">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7918">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7918">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7919">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7919">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7920">Esiska: sju siffror och en bokstav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7920">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7921">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7921">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7922">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7922">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7923">Non-Denesiska och enheter av senesiska: nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7923">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7924">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7924">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7925">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7925">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7926">Ej tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7926">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7927">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7927">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7928">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7929">Regex eller  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  hittar innehåll som matchar `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7929">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7930">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7930">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7931">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7931">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7932">Regex eller  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` hittar innehåll som matchar `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7932">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="medicare-beneficiary-identifier-mbi-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7965">MBI-kort (Identifier Identifier)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7965">Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7966">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7966">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7967">eleven character alphanumeric pattern</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7967">eleven character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7968">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7968">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7969">en siffra mellan 1 och 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7969">one digit between 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7970">en bokstav utom S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7970">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7971">en siffra eller bokstav utom S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7971">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7972">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7972">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7973">ett valfritt bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7973">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7974">en bokstav utom S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7974">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7975">en siffra eller bokstav utom S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7975">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7976">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7976">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7977">ett valfritt bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7977">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7978">två bokstäver utom S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7978">two letters excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7979">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7979">two digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7980">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7981">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7981">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7982">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7983">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7984">Det reguljära  `Regex_mbi_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7984">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7985">Ett nyckelord  `Keyword_mbi_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7985">A keyword from  `Keyword_mbi_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7986">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7987">Det reguljära  `Regex_mbi_card` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7987">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card -->
      <Entity id="f753a286-f5cc-47e6-a592-4be25fd02591" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7988">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7988">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mbi_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7989">Keyword_mbi_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7989">Keyword_mbi_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7990">mbi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7990">mbi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7991">mbi #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7991">mbi#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7992">medicare-mottagare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7992">medicare beneficiary #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7993">medicare identifier</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7993">medicare beneficiary identifier</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7994">medicare mottagarnr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7994">medicare beneficiary no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7995">medicare mottagarnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7995">medicare beneficiary number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7996">medicare-mottagare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7996">medicare beneficiary#</span></span>


## <a name="mexico-unique-population-registry-code-curp"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7997">Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7997">Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7998">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7998">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-7999">18 tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-7999">18 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8000">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8000">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8001">fyra bokstäver (inkänsliga versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8001">four letters (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8002">Sex siffror som anger ett giltigt datum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8002">six digits indicating a valid date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8003">en bokstav – H/h eller M/m</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8003">a letter - H/h or M/m</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8004">Två bokstäver som anger en giltig statuskod i Mexico</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8004">two letters indicating a valid Mexican state code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8005">tre bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8005">three letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8006">en bokstav eller en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8006">one letter or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8007">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8007">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8008">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8008">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8009">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8009">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8010">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8010">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8011">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8011">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8012">Funktionen hittar  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8012">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8013">Ett nyckelord  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8013">A keyword from  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8014">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8014">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8015">Funktionen hittar  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8015">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP) -->
      <Entity id="e905ad4d-5a74-406d-bf36-b1efca798af4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8036">Nederländska medborgares servicenummer (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8036">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8037">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8037">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8038">Åtta eller nio siffror som innehåller valfria blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8038">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8039">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8039">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8040">åtta-nio siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8040">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8041">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8041">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8042">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8042">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8043">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8043">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8044">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8044">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8045">två-tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8045">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8046">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8046">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8047">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8047">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8048">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8048">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8049">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8049">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8050">Funktionen för Func_netherlands_bsn hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8050">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8051">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_netherlands_bsn hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8051">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8052">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8052">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8076">Nederländska körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8076">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8077">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8078">tio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8078">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8079">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8080">tio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8080">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8081">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8081">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8082">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8082">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8083">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8083">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8084">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8084">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8085">Det reguljära  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8085">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8086">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8086">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
