## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8214">Nederländska passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8214">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8215">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8215">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8216">Nio bokstäver eller siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8216">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8217">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8217">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8218">nio bokstäver eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8218">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8219">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8220">inte tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8220">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8221">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8222">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8222">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8223">Det reguljära  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8223">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8224">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8224">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8225">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i formatet `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Exempel - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8225">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8226">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8227">Det reguljära  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8227">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8228">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8228">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8247">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8247">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8248">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8248">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8252">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8252">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8253">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8253">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8255">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8255">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8256">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8256">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8257">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8257">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8258">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8258">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8259">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8259">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8260">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8260">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8261">Funktionen hittar  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8261">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8262">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8262">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8263">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8263">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8264">Funktionen hittar  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8264">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8302">Nederländska momsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8302">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8303">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8303">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8304">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8304">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8305">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8305">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8306">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8306">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8307">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8307">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8308">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8308">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8309">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8309">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8310">14 tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8310">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8311">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8311">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8312">Alfanumeriskt mönster med 14 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8312">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8313">N eller n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8313">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8314">L eller l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8314">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8315">Valfritt blanksteg, punkt eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8315">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8316">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8316">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8317">Valfritt blanksteg, punkt eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8317">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8318">B eller b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8318">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8319">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8319">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8320">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8320">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8321">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8321">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8322">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8322">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8323">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8323">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8324">Funktionen Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8324">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8325">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8325">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8326">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8326">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8327">Funktionen Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8327">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8337">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8337">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8339">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8339">communication compliance policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8343">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8343">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8344">14-siffrigt till 16-siffrigt mönster med valfri avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8344">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8345">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8345">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8346">14-siffrigt till 16-siffrigt mönster med valfri avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8346">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8347">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8347">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8348">Ett valfritt bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8348">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8349">tre till fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8349">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8350">Ett valfritt bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8350">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8351">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8351">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8352">Ett valfritt bindestreck eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8352">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8353">Två till tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8353">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8354">Ett bindestreck eller blanksteg för alternativ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8354">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8355">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8355">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8356">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8356">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8357">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8357">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8358">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8358">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8359">Funktionen Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8359">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8360">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8360">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8361">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8361">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8362">Funktionen Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8362">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8377">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8377">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8378">åtta tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8378">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8379">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8379">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8380">åtta tecken för alfanumeriskt mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8380">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8381">två bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8381">two letters</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8383">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8383">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8384">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8384">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8385">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8385">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8386">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8386">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8387">Funktionen Func_newzealand_driver_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8387">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8388">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8388">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8389">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8389">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8390">Funktionen Func_newzealand_driver_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8390">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8461">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8461">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8462">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8462">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8463">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8463">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8464">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8464">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8465">Åtta eller nio siffror med valfria avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8465">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8466">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8466">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8467">Åtta eller nio siffror med valfria avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8467">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8468">två eller tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8468">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8469">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8469">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8470">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8470">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8471">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8471">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8472">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8472">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8473">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8474">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8474">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8475">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8476">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8476">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8477">Funktionen för Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8477">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8478">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8478">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8479">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8479">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8480">Funktionen för Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8480">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8489">Nya Zeeland med hälsonummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8489">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8490">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8490">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8491">tre bokstäver, ett blanksteg (valfritt) och fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8491">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8492">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8492">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8493">Tre bokstäver (inte ärendekänsliga) förutom "I" och "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8493">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8494">ett blanksteg (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8494">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8495">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8495">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8496">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8496">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8497">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8497">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8498">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8498">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8499">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8499">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8500">Funktionen Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8500">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8501">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_nz_terms hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8501">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8502">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8502">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8503">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8503">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8504">Funktionen Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8504">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8505">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8505">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8520">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8520">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8521">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8521">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8522">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8522">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8523">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8523">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8524">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8524">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8525">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8525">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8526">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8526">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8527">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8527">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8528">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8528">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8529">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8529">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8530">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8530">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8531">Ett valfritt bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8531">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8532">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8532">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8533">Ett valfritt bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8533">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8534">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8534">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8535">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8535">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8536">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8536">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8537">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8537">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8538">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8538">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8539">Funktionen för Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8539">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8540">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8540">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8541">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8541">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8542">Funktionen för Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8542">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8550">Id-nummer för Norge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8550">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8551">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8552">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8552">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8553">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8554">11 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8554">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8555">Sex siffror i formatet DDMMYY som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8555">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8556">tresiffrigt enskilt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8556">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8557">två kontrollsiffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8557">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8558">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8558">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8559">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8559">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8560">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8560">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8561">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8561">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8562">Funktionen för Func_norway_id_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8562">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8563">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_norway_id_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8563">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8564">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8564">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8565">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8565">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8566">Funktionen Func_norway_id_numbe hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8566">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8567">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8567">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8576">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8576">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8577">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8578">12 siffror avgränsade med bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8578">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8579">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8580">12 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8580">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8581">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8581">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8582">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8582">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8583">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8583">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8584">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8584">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8585">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8585">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8586">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8586">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8587">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8587">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8588">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8588">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8589">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8589">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8590">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_philippines_unified_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8590">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8591">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_philippines_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8591">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8598">Polens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8598">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8599">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8599">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8600">14 siffror med två snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8600">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8601">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8601">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8602">14 siffror och två snedstreck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8602">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8603">fem siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8603">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8604">ett snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8604">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8605">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8605">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8606">ett snedstreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8606">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8607">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8607">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8608">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8608">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8609">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8609">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8610">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8610">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8611">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8611">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8612">Det reguljära  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8612">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8613">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8613">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8737">Polens identitetskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8737">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8738">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8738">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8739">tre bokstäver och sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8739">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8740">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8740">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8741">Tre bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga) följt av sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8741">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8742">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8742">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8743">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8743">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8744">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8744">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8745">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8745">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8746">Funktionen för Func_polish_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8746">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8747">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8747">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8748">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8748">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8749">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8749">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8750">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8750">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8753">Wa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8753">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8754">Wa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8754">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8755">Wa i nr dowodu to isamoxoci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8755">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8756">Dowód Toósamoòci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8756">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>

## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8759">Polens national-ID (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8759">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8760">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8760">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8761">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8761">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8762">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8762">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8763">Sex siffror som representerar födelsedatum i formatet YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8763">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8764">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8764">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8765">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8765">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8766">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8766">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8767">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8767">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8768">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8768">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8769">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8769">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8770">Funktionen för Func_pesel_identification_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8770">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8771">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_pesel_identification_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8771">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8772">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8772">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8773">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8773">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8774">Funktionen för Func_pesel_identification_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8774">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8775">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8775">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8787">Polen passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8787">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8788">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i typen Känslig information i EU Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8788">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8789">Det är tillgängligt som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8789">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8790">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8790">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8791">Två bokstäver och sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8791">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8792">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8792">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8793">Två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga) följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8793">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8794">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8794">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8795">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8795">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8796">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8796">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8797">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8797">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8798">Funktionen hittar `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8798">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8799">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8799">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8800">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8800">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8801">Ett nyckelord `Keywords_eu_passport_date` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8801">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8802">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8802">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8803">Funktionen hittar `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8803">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8804">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8804">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8805">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8805">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8806">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8806">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8807">Funktionen hittar `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8807">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8808">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8808">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8834">PolenS REGON-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8834">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8835">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8835">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8836">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8836">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8837">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8837">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8838">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8838">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8839">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8839">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8840">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8840">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8841">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8841">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8842">9- eller 14-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8842">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8843">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8843">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8844">Nio eller fyrsiffriga siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8844">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8845">nio siffror eller</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8845">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8846">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8846">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8847">bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8847">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8848">fem siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8848">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8849">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8849">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8850">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8850">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8851">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8851">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8852">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8852">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8853">Funktionen för Func_polish_regon_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8853">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8854">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_polish_regon_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8854">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8855">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8855">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8856">Funktionen för Func_polish_regon_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8856">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8865">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8865">regonno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8866">företags-ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8866">company id</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8873">Polens skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8873">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8874">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8874">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8875">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8875">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8876">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8876">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8877">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8877">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8878">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8878">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8879">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8879">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8880">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8880">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8881">11 siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8881">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8882">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8882">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8883">11 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8883">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8884">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8884">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8885">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8885">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8886">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8886">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8887">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8887">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8888">Funktionen hittar  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8888">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8889">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8889">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8919">Portugal med kreditkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8919">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8920">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8920">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8921">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8921">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8922">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8922">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8923">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8923">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8924">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8924">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8925">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8925">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8926">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8926">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8927">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8927">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8928">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_portugal_citizen_card hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8928">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8929">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_portugal_citizen_card hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8929">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8949">Portugals körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8949">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8950">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8950">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8951">två mönster – två bokstäver följt av 5–8 siffror med specialtecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8951">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8952">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8952">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8953">Mönster 1: Två bokstäver följt av 5/6 med specialtecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8953">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8954">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8954">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8955">Ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8955">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8956">Fem eller sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8956">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8957">Ett blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8957">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8958">En siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8958">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8959">Mönster 2: En bokstav följt av 6/8 siffror med specialtecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8959">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8960">En bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8960">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8961">Ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8961">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8962">Sex eller åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8962">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8963">Ett blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8963">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8964">En siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8964">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8965">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8965">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8966">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8966">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8967">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8967">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8968">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8968">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8969">Det reguljära  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8969">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-8970">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-8970">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9102">Portugal passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9102">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9103">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9103">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9104">en bokstav följt av sex siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9104">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9105">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9105">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9106">en bokstav följt av sex siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9106">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9107">en bokstav (inte en ärendekänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9107">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9108">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9108">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9109">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9109">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9110">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9110">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9111">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9111">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9112">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9112">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9113">Det reguljära  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9113">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9114">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9114">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9115">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9115">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9116">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9116">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9117">Det reguljära  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9117">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9118">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9118">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
