## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9145">Portugals skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9145">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9146">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9146">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9147">Nio siffror med valfria blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9147">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9148">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9148">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9149">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9149">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9150">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9150">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9151">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9151">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9152">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9152">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9153">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9153">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9154">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9154">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9155">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9155">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9156">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9156">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9157">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9157">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9158">Funktionen hittar  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9158">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9159">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9159">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9160">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9160">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9161">Funktionen hittar  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9161">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9186">Rumäniens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9186">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9187">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9188">ett tecken följt av åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9188">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9189">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9190">ett tecken följt av åtta siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9190">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9191">en bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig) eller en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9191">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9192">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9192">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9193">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9193">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9194">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9194">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9195">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9195">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9196">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9196">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9197">Det reguljära  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9197">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9198">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9198">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9326">Rumäniens personliga numeriska kod (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9326">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9327">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9327">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9328">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9328">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9329">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9329">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9330">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9330">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9331">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9331">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9332">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9332">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9333">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9333">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9334">13 siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9334">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9335">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9335">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9336">en siffra från 1–9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9336">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9337">Sex siffror som representerar födelsedatum (DSMMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9337">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9338">två siffror, som kan vara 01-52 eller 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9338">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9339">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9339">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9340">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9341">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9341">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9342">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9343">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9343">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9344">Funktionen hittar  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9344">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9345">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9345">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9346">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9346">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9347">Funktionen hittar  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9347">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9398">Rumänien, passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9398">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9399">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9399">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9400">Åtta eller nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9400">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9401">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9401">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9402">Åtta eller nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9402">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9403">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9403">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9404">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9404">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9405">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9405">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9406">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9406">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9407">Det reguljära  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9407">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9408">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9408">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9409">Det reguljära uttrycket hittar datum i `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` formatet DD MMM/MMM YY (Exempel- 01 FEB/10 FEB) eller ett nyckelord `Keywords_eu_passport_date` från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9409">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9410">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9410">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9411">Det reguljära  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9411">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9412">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9412">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9431">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9431">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9432">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9432">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9433">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9433">communication compliance policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9437">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9438">10-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9438">10-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9439">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9440">10-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9440">10-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9443">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9443">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9444">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9444">an optional space</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9447">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9447">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9448">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9448">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9449">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9449">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9450">Regex-Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9450">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9451">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9451">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9468">Ryssland passnummer internationellt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9468">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9469">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9469">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9470">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9470">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9471">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9471">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9472">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9472">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9473">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9473">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9474">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9474">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9475">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9476">niosiffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9476">nine-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9477">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9477">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9478">niosiffriga nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9478">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9479">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9479">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9480">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9480">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9481">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9481">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9482">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9482">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9483">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9483">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9484">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9485">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9485">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9486">Regex-Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9486">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9487">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9487">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9504">Saudiarabiens national-ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9504">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9505">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9505">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9506">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9506">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9507">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9507">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9508">10 siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9508">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9509">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9509">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9510">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9510">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9511">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9511">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9512">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9512">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9513">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9513">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9514">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9514">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9521">Nummer till Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9521">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9522">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9522">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9523">nio bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9523">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9524">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9524">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9525">Nio bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9525">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9526">bokstaven "F", "G", "S" eller "T" (inte ärendekänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9526">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9527">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9527">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9528">en alfabetisk kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9528">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9529">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9530">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9530">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9531">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9532">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9532">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9533">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_singapore_nric hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9533">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9534">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_singapore_nric hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9534">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9535">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9535">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9536">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9536">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9537">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_singapore_nric hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9537">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9538">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9538">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9549">Slovakiens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9549">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9550">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9550">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9551">ett tecken följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9551">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9552">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9552">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9553">ett tecken följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9553">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9554">en bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig) eller en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9554">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9555">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9555">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9556">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9556">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9557">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9557">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9558">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9558">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9559">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9559">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9560">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9560">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9561">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9561">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9693">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9693">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9694">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9694">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9695">nio eller tio siffror som innehåller valfritt omslag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9695">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9696">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9696">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9697">Sex siffror som representerar födelsedatum</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9697">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9698">valfritt snedstreck (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9698">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9699">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9699">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9700">en valfri kontrollsiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9700">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9701">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9701">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9702">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9702">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9703">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9703">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9704">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9704">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9705">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9705">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9706">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9706">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9707">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9707">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9708">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9708">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9755">Slovakiens passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9755">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9756">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9757">en siffra eller bokstav följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9757">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9758">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9759">en siffra eller bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig) följt av sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9759">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9760">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9760">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9761">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9761">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9762">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9762">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9763">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9763">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9764">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9764">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9765">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9765">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9766">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9766">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9767">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9767">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9768">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9768">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9769">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9769">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9791">Sloveniens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9791">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9792">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9792">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9793">Nio siffror utan blanksteg och avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9793">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9794">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9794">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9795">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9795">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9798">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9798">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9799">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9799">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9800">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9800">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9801">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9801">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9928">Slovenska unik master number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9928">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9929">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9929">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9930">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9930">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9931">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9931">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9932">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9932">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9933">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9933">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9934">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9934">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9935">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9935">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9936">13 siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9936">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9937">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9937">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9938">13 siffror i det angivna mönstret:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9938">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9939">sju siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (DDMMLLL) där "LLL" motsvarar de tre sista siffrorna i födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9939">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9940">två siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9940">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9941">Tre siffror som motsvarar en kombination av kön och serienummer för personer som föds på samma dag (000-499 för man och 500-999 för kvinna)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9941">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9942">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9942">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9943">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9943">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9944">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9944">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9945">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9945">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9946">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9946">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9947">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9947">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9948">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9948">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9949">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9949">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9950">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9950">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9978">Slovenska passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9978">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9979">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9979">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9980">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9980">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9981">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9981">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9982">Två bokstäver följt av sju siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9982">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9983">bokstaven "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9983">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9984">en versal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9984">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9985">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9985">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9986">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9986">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9987">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9987">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9988">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9988">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9989">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9989">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9990">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9990">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9991">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9991">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9992">Det reguljära `Regex_eu_passport_date1` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD.MM.YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9992">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9993">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9993">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9994">Det reguljära  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9994">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-9995">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-9995">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10018">Slovenska skatteidentifieringsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10018">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10019">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10019">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10020">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10020">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10021">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10021">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10022">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10022">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10023">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10023">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10024">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10024">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10025">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10025">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10026">Åtta siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10026">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10027">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10027">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10028">en siffra från 1–9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10028">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10029">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10029">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10030">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10030">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10031">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10031">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10032">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10032">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10033">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10033">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10034">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10034">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10035">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10035">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10036">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10036">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10037">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10037">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10038">Funktionen hittar  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10038">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10062">South Africa identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10062">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10063">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10063">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10064">13 siffror som kan innehålla blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10064">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10065">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10065">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10066">13 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10066">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10067">Sex siffror i formatet YYMMDD, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10067">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10068">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10068">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10069">en ensiffrig indikator</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10069">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10070">siffran "8" eller "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10070">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10071">en siffra, som är en kontrollsummasiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10071">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10072">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10072">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10073">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10073">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10074">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10074">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10075">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10075">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10076">Funktionen för Func_south_africa_identification_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10076">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10077">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_south_africa_identification_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10077">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10078">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10078">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10079">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10079">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10084">Registreringsnummer för sydkoreanska invånare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10084">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10085">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10085">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10086">13 siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10086">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10087">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10087">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10088">13 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10088">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10089">Sex siffror i formatet YYMMDD, som är födelsedatumet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10089">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10090">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10090">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10091">en siffra som bestäms av talet och kön</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10091">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10092">fyrsiffrig födelsedatumskod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10092">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10093">en siffra som används för att särskilja personer som de föregående siffrorna är identiska för</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10093">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10094">en kontrollsiffra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10094">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10095">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10095">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10096">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10096">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10097">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10097">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10098">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10098">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10099">Funktionen för Func_south_korea_resident_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10099">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10100">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_south_korea_resident_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10100">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10101">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10101">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10102">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10102">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10103">Funktionen för Func_south_korea_resident_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10103">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10104">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10104">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10112">Spaniens körkortsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10112">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10113">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10113">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10114">Åtta siffror följt av ett tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10114">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10115">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10115">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10116">Åtta siffror följt av ett tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10116">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10117">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10117">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10118">en siffra eller bokstav (inte en teckenkänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10118">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10119">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10119">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10120">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10120">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10121">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10122">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10122">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10123">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10123">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10124">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10124">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10125">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10125">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10126">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10126">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10260">Spanien DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10260">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10261">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10261">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10262">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10262">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10263">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10263">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10264">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10264">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10265">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10265">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10266">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10266">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10267">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10268">Åtta siffror följt av ett tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10268">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10269">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10270">sju siffror följt av ett tecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10270">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10271">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10271">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10272">Ett valfritt blanksteg eller bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10272">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10273">en bkryssbokstav (inte fallkänslig)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10273">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10274">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10275">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10275">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10276">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10277">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10277">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10278">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10278">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10279">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10279">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10280">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10280">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10281">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10281">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
