## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10305">Spanien passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10305">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10306">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10306">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10307">En kombination av åtta eller nio tecken med bokstäver och siffror utan blanksteg eller avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10307">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10308">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10308">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10309">En kombination av åtta eller nio tecken med bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10309">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10310">två siffror eller bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10310">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10311">en siffra eller bokstav (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10311">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10312">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10312">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10313">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10313">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10314">Ej tillämpligt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10314">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10315">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10315">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10316">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10316">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10317">Det reguljära  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10317">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10318">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10318">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10319">Det reguljära `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` uttrycket hittar datum i formatet DD-MM-YYYY eller ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_date` hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10319">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10320">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10320">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10321">Det reguljära  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10321">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10322">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10322">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10351">Spaniens personnummer (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10351">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10352">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10352">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10353">11–12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10353">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10354">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10354">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10355">11–12 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10355">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10356">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10356">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10357">ett snedstreck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10357">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10358">sju till åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10358">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10359">ett snedstreck (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10359">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10360">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10360">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10361">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10362">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10362">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10363">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10364">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10364">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10365">Funktionen för Func_spanish_social_security_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10365">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10366">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10366">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10367">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10367">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10368">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10368">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10369">Funktionen för Func_spanish_social_security_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10369">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10370">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10370">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10379">Skatteidentifieringsnummer för Spanien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10379">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10380">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10380">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10381">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10381">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10382">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10382">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10383">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10383">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10384">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10384">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10385">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10385">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10386">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10386">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10387">sju eller åtta siffror och en eller två bokstäver i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10387">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10388">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10388">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10389">Spanska naturliga personer med ett Spanien National Identity Card:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10389">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10390">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10390">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10391">en versaler (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10391">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10392">Non-resident Sstraards utan ett Spain National Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10392">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10393">en versaler "L" (gemener/versaler) (gemener/VERSALER) (gemener och versaler) (gemener/VERSALER)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10393">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10394">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10394">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10395">en versaler (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10395">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10396">Invånare som är under 14 år utan spaniens nationalidentitetskort:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10396">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10397">en versal "K" (gemener/versaler) (gemener och versaler) (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10397">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10398">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10398">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10399">en versaler (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10399">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10400">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10400">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10401">en versal som är "X", "Y" eller "Z" (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10401">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10402">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10402">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10403">en versaler (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10403">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10404">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10404">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10405">en versal som är "M" (gemener/versaler) (gemener och versaler) (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10405">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10406">sju siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10406">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10407">en versaler (gemener och versaler)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10407">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10408">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10408">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10409">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10409">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10410">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10410">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10411">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10411">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10412">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10412">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10413">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10413">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10414">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10414">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10415">Funktionen eller  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` hittar innehåll som matchar `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10415">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10446">SQL Server en anslutningssträng</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10446">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10447">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10447">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10448">Strängen "Användar-ID", "Användar-ID", "uid" eller "UserId" följt av de tecken och strängar som beskrivs i mönstret nedan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10448">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10449">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10449">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10450">strängen "Användar-ID", "Användar-ID", "uid" eller "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10450">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10451">valfri kombination av 1–200 gemener eller versaler, siffror, symboler, specialtecken eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10451">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10452">strängen "Lösenord" eller "pwd" där "pwd" inte föregås av en gemener</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10452">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10453">Ett likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10453">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10454">alla tecken som inte är ett dollartecken ($), procenttecken (%) större än symbol (>), symbol (@), citattecken ("), semikolon (;), vänster klammerparentes([) eller vänster klammerparentes ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10454">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10455">valfri kombination av 7–128 tecken som inte är ett semikolon (;), snedstreck (/) eller citattecken (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10455">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10456">Semikolon (;) eller citattecken (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10456">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10457">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10457">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10458">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10458">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10459">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10459">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10460">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10460">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10461">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10461">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10462">Ett nyckelord CEP_GlobalFilter hittades inte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10462">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10463">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10463">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10464">Det reguljära uttrycket CEP_CommonExampleKeywords hittar inte innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10464">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10465">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10465">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10466">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10466">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10467">some-password</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10467">some-password</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10472">(Tekniskt sett identifierar den här typen av känslig information dessa nyckelord med hjälp av ett reguljärt uttryck, inte en nyckelordslista.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10472">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10473">Lösenord eller pwd följt av 0-2 blanksteg, ett likhetstecken (=), 0-2 blanksteg och en asterisk (\*) -ELLER-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10473">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10474">Lösenord eller pwd följt av:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10474">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10475">Likhetstecken (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10475">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10476">Mindre än-symbol (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10476">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10477">En kombination av 1–200 tecken som är versaler eller gemener, siffror, asterisk (\*), bindestreck (-), understrykning (_) eller blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10477">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10478">Större än-symbol (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10478">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10479">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10479">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10492">Sverigedrivrutinens licensnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10492">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10493">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10493">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10494">tio siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10494">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10495">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10495">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10496">tio siffror som innehåller ett bindestreck:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10496">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10497">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10497">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10498">ett bindestreck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10498">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10499">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10499">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10500">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10500">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10501">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10501">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10502">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10502">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10503">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10503">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10504">Det reguljära  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` uttrycket hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10504">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10505">Ett nyckelord från  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` eller `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10505">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10638">National ID för Sverige</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10638">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10639">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10640">10 eller 12 siffror och en valfri avgränsare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10640">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10641">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10642">10 eller 12 siffror och en valfri avgränsare:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10642">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10643">två siffror (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10643">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10644">Sex siffror i datumformat YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10644">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10645">avgränsare av "-" eller "+" (valfritt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10645">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10646">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10646">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10647">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10647">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10648">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10648">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10649">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10649">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10650">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10650">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10651">Funktionen hittar `Func_swedish_national_identifier` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10651">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10652">Ett nyckelord `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10652">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10653">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10653">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10654">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10654">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10655">Funktionen hittar `Func_swedish_national_identifier` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10655">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10656">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10656">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10675">Sverige passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10675">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10676">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10676">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10677">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10677">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10678">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10678">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10679">åtta siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10679">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10680">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10681">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10681">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10682">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10683">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10683">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10684">det reguljära uttrycket Regex_sweden_passport_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10684">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10685">ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_sweden_passport` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10685">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10686">det reguljära uttrycket hittar ett datum i formatet `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) eller ett `Keywords_eu_passport_date` nyckelord från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10686">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10687">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10687">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10688">det reguljära uttrycket Regex_sweden_passport_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10688">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10689">ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keyword_sweden_passport` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10689">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10725">Skatteidentifieringsnummer i Sverige</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10725">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10726">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10726">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10727">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10727">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10728">policyer för kommunikationsefterlevnad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10728">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10729">informationsstyrning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10729">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10730">hantering av arkivhandlingar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10730">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10731">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10731">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10732">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10732">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10733">10 siffror och en symbol i det angivna mönstret</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10733">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10734">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10734">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10735">10 siffror och en symbol:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10735">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10736">Sex siffror som motsvarar födelsedatumet (AMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10736">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10737">ett plustecken eller minustecken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10737">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10738">Tre siffror som gör ID-numret unikt där:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10738">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10739">för nummer som utfärdats före 1990, den sjunde och åttonde siffran identifiera födelsedatum eller foreign-born people</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10739">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10740">Siffran i den nionde positionen anger kön med antingen udda för man eller till och med för kvinna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10740">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10741">en checksiffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10741">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10742">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10742">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10743">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10743">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10744">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10744">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10745">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10745">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10746">Funktionen hittar  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10746">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10747">Ett nyckelord  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10747">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10748">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10748">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10749">Funktionen hittar  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10749">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10775">SWIFT-kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10775">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10776">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10776">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10777">fyra bokstäver följt av 5–31 bokstäver eller siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10777">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10778">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10778">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10779">fyra bokstäver följt av 5–31 bokstäver eller siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10779">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10780">bankkod på fyra bokstäver (inte ärendekänsligt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10780">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10781">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10781">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10782">4–28 bokstäver eller siffror (BBAN (Basic Bank Account Number))</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10782">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10783">ett valfritt blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10783">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10784">en till tre bokstäver eller siffror (resten av BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10784">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10785">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10785">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10786">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10786">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10787">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10787">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10788">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10788">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10789">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_swift hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10789">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10790">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_swift hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10790">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10828">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10828">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10833">Säkerhet för Microsoft-molnappen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10833">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10834">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10834">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10835">13-siffrigt nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10835">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10836">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10836">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10837">13-siffrigt nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10837">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10838">tre siffror – 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10838">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10839">en valfri punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10839">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10840">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10840">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10841">en valfri punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10841">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10842">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10842">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10843">en valfri punkt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10843">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10844">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10844">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10845">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10845">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10846">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10846">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10847">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10847">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10848">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10848">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10849">Funktionen för Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10849">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10850">Ett nyckelord från Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10850">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10851">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10851">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10852">Funktionen för Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10852">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10873">Taiwans national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10873">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10874">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10874">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10875">en bokstav (på engelska) följt av nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10875">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10876">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10876">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10877">en bokstav (på engelska) följt av nio siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10877">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10878">en bokstav (på engelska, inte den där den är det.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10878">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10879">siffran "1" eller "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10879">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10880">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10880">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10881">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10881">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10882">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10882">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10883">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10883">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10884">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10884">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10885">Funktionen för Func_taiwanese_national_id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10885">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10886">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_taiwanese_national_id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10886">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10887">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10887">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10888">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10888">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10907">Taiwan passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10907">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10908">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10908">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10909">biometrisk passnummer: nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10909">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10910">icke-biometrisk passnummer: nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10910">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10911">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10911">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10912">biometrisk pass nummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10912">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10913">tecknet "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10913">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10914">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10914">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10915">icke-biometrisk passnummer:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10915">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10916">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10916">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10917">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10917">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10918">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10918">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10919">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10919">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10920">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10920">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10921">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_taiwan_passport hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10921">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10922">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_taiwan_passport hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10922">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10933">Taiwan-intjänat certifikat (ARC/TARC) nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10933">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10934">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10934">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10935">10 bokstäver och siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10935">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10936">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10936">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10937">10 bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10937">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10938">Två bokstäver (inte versaler och teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10938">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10939">åtta siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10939">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10940">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10940">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10941">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10941">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10942">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10942">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10943">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10943">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10944">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10944">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10945">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10945">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10959">Identifieringskod för thailändska</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10959">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10960">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10960">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10961">13 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10961">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10962">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10962">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10963">13 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10963">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10964">första siffran är inte noll eller nio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10964">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10965">12 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10965">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10966">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10966">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10967">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10967">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10968">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10968">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10969">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10969">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10970">Funktionen för Func_Thai_Citizen_Id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10970">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10971">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10971">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10972">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10972">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10973">Funktionen för Func_Thai_Citizen_Id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10973">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10988">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10988">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10989">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10989">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10990">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10990">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10991">Funktionen för Func_Turkish_National_Id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10991">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10992">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_Turkish_National_Id hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10992">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10993">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10993">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-10994">Funktionen för Func_Turkish_National_Id hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-10994">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11001">Storbritannien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11001">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11002">driver's license number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11002">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11003">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11003">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11004">Kombination av 18 bokstäver och siffror i det angivna formatet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11004">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11005">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11005">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11006">18 bokstäver och siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11006">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11007">Fem bokstäver (inte ärendekänsliga) eller siffran "9" i stället för en bokstav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11007">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11008">En siffra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11008">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11009">Fem siffror i datumformatet MMDDY för födelsedatumet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11009">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11010">Det sjunde tecknet ökas med 50 om drivrutinen är kvinna. för prov, 51 till 62 i stället för 01 till 12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11010">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11011">Två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga) eller siffran "9" i stället för en bokstav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11011">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11012">Fem siffror.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11012">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11013">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11013">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11014">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11014">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11015">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11015">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11016">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11016">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11017">Funktionen hittar `Func_uk_drivers_license` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11017">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11018">Ett nyckelord `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` från hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11018">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11019">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11019">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11020">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11020">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11021">Funktionen hittar `Func_uk_drivers_license` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11021">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11022">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11022">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11143">Storbritannien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11143">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11144">nummer för att samla, rulla ut, 75</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11144">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11145">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11145">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11146">två bokstäver följt av 1–4 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11146">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11147">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11147">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11148">Två bokstäver (inte teckenkänsliga) följt av 1–4 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11148">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11149">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11149">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11150">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11150">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11151">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11151">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11152">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11152">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11153">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_uk_electoral hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11153">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11154">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_uk_electoral hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11154">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11155">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11155">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11156">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11156">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11157">mötesmöte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11157">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11158">formulär för att skapa en 20</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11158">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11159">register över registrering av registrer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11159">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11160">roll för underse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11160">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11161">Storbritannien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11161">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11162">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11162">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11163">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11164">10–17 siffror avgränsade med blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11164">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11165">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11166">10–17 siffror:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11166">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11167">antingen 3 eller 10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11167">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11168">ett blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11168">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11169">tre siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11169">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11170">ett blanksteg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11170">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11171">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11171">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11172">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11173">Ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11173">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11174">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11175">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11175">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11176">Funktionen för Func_uk_nhs_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11176">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11177">Något av följande är sant:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11177">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11178">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_uk_nhs_number hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11178">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11179">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11179">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11180">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11180">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11181">Kontrollsumman passeras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11181">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
