## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11199">Storbritannien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11199">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11200">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11200">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11201">Den här typen av känslig information ingår i den nationella identifieringstypen (EU).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11201">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11202">Det är tillgängligt som en fristående typ av känslig information.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11202">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11203">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11203">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11204">Sju tecken eller nio tecken avgränsade med blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11204">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11205">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11205">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11206">två möjliga mönster:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11206">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11207">två bokstäver (giltiga NINOs använder bara vissa tecken i det här prefixet, som det här mönstret verifierar, inte de är det.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11207">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11208">sex siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11208">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11209">antingen "A", "B", "C" eller "D" (t.ex. prefixet tillåts bara vissa tecken i suffixet, inte teckenkänsliga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11209">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11210">ELLER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11210">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11211">två bokstäver</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11211">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11212">blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11212">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11213">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11213">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11214">blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11214">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11215">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11215">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11216">blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11216">a space or dash</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11222">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11222">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11223">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11223">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11224">Funktionen för Func_uk_nino hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11224">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11225">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_uk_nino hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11225">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11226">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11227">Funktionen för Func_uk_nino hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11227">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11251">Den här typen av känslig information kan bara användas i:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11251">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11252">principer för dataförlustskydd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11252">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11257">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11257">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11260">10 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11260">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11261">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11264">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11264">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11265">Funktionen hittar  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11265">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />

      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11286">U.S. bank account number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11286">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11287">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11287">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11288">6-17 siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11288">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11289">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11289">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11291">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11292">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11292">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11293">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11294">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11294">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11295">Det reguljära uttrycket Regex_usa_bank_account_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11295">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11296">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_usa_Bank_Account hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11296">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11327">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11327">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11328">Beror på delstat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11328">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11329">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11329">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11330">beror på delstat – till exempel New York:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11330">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11331">Nio siffror med formatet sss sss sss matchar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11331">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11332">Nio siffror med ssssssssss matchar inte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11332">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11333">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11333">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11334">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11334">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11335">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11335">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11336">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11336">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11337">Funktionen för Func_new_york_drivers_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11337">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11338">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11338">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11339">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_us_drivers_license hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11339">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11340">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11340">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11341">Funktionen för Func_new_york_drivers_license_number hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11341">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11342">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11342">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11343">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11343">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11344">Inget nyckelord från Keyword_us_drivers_license hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11344">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11442">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11442">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11443">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11444">Nio siffror som börjar med "9" och innehåller "7" eller "8" som fjärde siffra, alternativt formaterade med blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11444">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11445">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11446">formaterat:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11446">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11447">siffran "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11447">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11448">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11448">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11449">blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11449">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11450">a "7" eller "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11450">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11451">en siffra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11451">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11452">blanksteg eller streck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11452">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11453">fyra siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11453">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11454">oformaterad:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11454">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11455">siffran "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11455">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11456">två siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11456">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11457">a "7" eller "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11457">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11458">fem siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11458">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11459">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11460">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11460">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11461">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11462">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11462">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11463">Funktionen för Func_formatted_itin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11463">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11464">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_itin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11464">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11465">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11465">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11466">Funktionen Func_unformatted_itin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11466">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11467">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_itin hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11467">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11468">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11468">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11469">Funktionen Func_formatted_itin eller Func_unformatted_itin hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11469">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11470">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11470">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11471">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11471">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11474">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11474">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11475">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11475">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11476">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11476">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11477">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11477">ssn</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11478">tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11478">tin</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11484">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11484">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11485">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11485">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11486">nio siffror, som kan vara i ett formaterat eller oformaterat mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11486">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11487">Om det har utfärdats före mitten av 2011 har SSN stark formatering där vissa delar av numret måste faller inom vissa intervall för att vara giltigt (men det finns ingen kontrollsumma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11487">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11488">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11488">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11489">fyra funktioner söker efter SSN i fyra olika mönster:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11489">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11490">Func_ssn söker efter SSN med stark formatering före 2011 som är formaterade med streck eller blanksteg (s-ss-s eller s)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11490">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11491">Func_unformatted_ssn söker efter SSN med stark formatering före 2011 som är oformaterade som nio siffror i följd (sss)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11491">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11492">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn söker efter SSN efter 2011 som är formaterade med streck eller blanksteg (s-ss-s eller s s)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11492">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11493">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn söker efter SSN efter 2011 som är oformaterade som nio siffror i följd (ss)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11493">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11494">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11495">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11495">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11496">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11497">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11497">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11498">Funktionen för Func_ssn hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11498">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11499">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ssn hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11499">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11500">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11500">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11501">Funktionen för Func_unformatted_ssn hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11501">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11502">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ssn hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11502">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11503">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11503">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11504">Funktionen Func_randomized_formatted_ssn hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11504">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11505">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ssn hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11505">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11506">En DLP-princip har låg konfidens för att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11506">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11507">Funktionen för Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11507">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11508">Ett nyckelord från Keyword_ssn hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11508">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11509">Nyckelord</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11509">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11510">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11510">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11511">SSA-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11511">SSA Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11513">social security #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11513">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11514">social security #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11514">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11515">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11515">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11516">Social Security #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11516">Social Security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11517">Soc Sec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11517">Soc Sec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11518">SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11518">SSN</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11519">SSNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11519">SSNS</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11520">SSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11520">SSN#</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11523">U.S. / Storbritannien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11523">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11524">passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11524">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11525">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11525">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11526">nio siffror</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11526">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11527">Mönster</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11527">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11528">nio siffror i följd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11528">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11529">Kontrollsumma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11530">Nej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11530">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11531">Definition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11532">En DLP-princip har hög säkerhet att den har upptäckt den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11532">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11533">Funktionen för Func_usa_uk_passport hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11533">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11534">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11534">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11535">Ett nyckelord `Keywords_eu_passport_date` från hittas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11535">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11536">En DLP-princip har med medelhög säkerhet identifierat den här typen av känslig information om följande inifrån 300 tecken:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11536">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11537">Funktionen för Func_usa_uk_passport hittar innehåll som matchar mönstret.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11537">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f4a0d-11538">Ett nyckelord från `Keywords_eu_passport_number` eller `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` hittas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f4a0d-11538">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
